402static void from_euler(const real_T euler_angle[3], real_T q[4])



403{



404  real_T cr2;



405  real_T cp2;



406  real_T cy2;



407  real_T sr2;



408  real_T sp2;



409  real_T sy2;



410  real_T q_tmp;



411  real_T q_tmp_0;



412  cr2 = cos(euler_angle[0] * 0.5);



413  cp2 = cos(euler_angle[1] * 0.5);



414  cy2 = cos(euler_angle[2] * 0.5);



415  sr2 = sin(euler_angle[0] * 0.5);



416  sp2 = sin(euler_angle[1] * 0.5);



417  sy2 = sin(euler_angle[2] * 0.5);



418  q_tmp = cr2 * cp2;



419  q_tmp_0 = sr2 * sp2;



420  q[0] = q_tmp * cy2 + q_tmp_0 * sy2;



421  cr2 *= sp2;



422  cp2 *= sr2;



423  q[1] = cp2 * cy2 - cr2 * sy2;



424  q[2] = cr2 * cy2 + cp2 * sy2;



425  q[3] = q_tmp * sy2 - q_tmp_0 * cy2;



426}

451  m[6] = (q2q4 + q1q3) * 2.0;

473static void from_rotation_matrix(const real_T m[9], real_T q[4])



474{



475  real_T tr;



476  tr = (m[0] + m[4]) + m[8];



477  if (tr > 0.0) {



478    tr = sqrt(tr + 1.0) * 2.0;



479    q[0] = 0.25 * tr;



480    q[1] = (m[5] - m[7]) / tr;



481    q[2] = (m[6] - m[2]) / tr;



482    q[3] = (m[1] - m[3]) / tr;



483  } else if ((m[0] > m[4]) && (m[0] > m[8])) {



484    tr = sqrt(((m[0] + 1.0) - m[4]) - m[8]) * 2.0;



485    q[0] = (m[5] - m[7]) / tr;



486    q[1] = 0.25 * tr;



487    q[2] = (m[3] + m[1]) / tr;



488    q[3] = (m[6] + m[2]) / tr;



489  } else if (m[4] > m[8]) {



490    tr = sqrt(((m[4] + 1.0) - m[0]) - m[8]) * 2.0;



491    q[0] = (m[6] - m[2]) / tr;



492    q[1] = (m[3] + m[1]) / tr;



493    q[2] = 0.25 * tr;



494    q[3] = (m[7] + m[5]) / tr;



495  } else {



496    tr = sqrt(((m[8] + 1.0) - m[0]) - m[4]) * 2.0;



497    q[0] = (m[1] - m[3]) / tr;



498    q[1] = (m[6] + m[2]) / tr;



499    q[2] = (m[7] + m[5]) / tr;



500    q[3] = 0.25 * tr;



501  }



502}

505static void set_throttle_out(real_T throttle_ini, real_T apply_angle_boost,



506  real_T filter_cutoff, DW *rtDW)



507{



508  real_T cos_tilt;



509  real_T amto;



510  cos_tilt = throttle_ini / (rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_CONTROL_ANGLE_LIMIT *



511    rtDW->throttle_thrust_max);



512  amto = cos_tilt;



513  if (cos_tilt < 0.0) {



514    amto = 0.0;



515  }



516



517  if (cos_tilt > 1.0) {



518    amto = 1.0;



519  }



520



521  rtDW->althold_lean_angle_max += rtDW->dt / (rtDW->dt + rtDW->angle_limit_tc) *



522    (acos(amto) - rtDW->althold_lean_angle_max);



523  if (rtDW->throttle_thrust_max == 0.0) {



524    rtDW->althold_lean_angle_max = 0.0;



525  }



526



527  rtDW->throttle_cutoff_frequency = filter_cutoff;



528  if ((apply_angle_boost != 0.0) && (rtDW->angle_boost_enabled != 0.0)) {



529    cos_tilt = cos(rtDW->pitch) * cos(rtDW->roll);



530    if (cos_tilt < 0.83) {



531      cos_tilt = 0.83;



532    }



533



534    throttle_ini /= cos_tilt;



535  }



536



537  rtDW->throttle_in = throttle_ini;



538  cos_tilt = fmax(throttle_ini, rtDW->throttle_in);



539  amto = cos_tilt;



540  if (cos_tilt < 0.0) {



541    amto = 0.0;



542  }



543



544  if (cos_tilt > 1.0) {



545    amto = 1.0;



546  }



547



548  cos_tilt = fmax(amto, fmax(0.0, 1.0 - rtDW->throttle_rpy_mix) * amto +



549                  rtDW->throttle_hover * rtDW->throttle_rpy_mix);



550  rtDW->throttle_avg_max = cos_tilt;



551  if (cos_tilt < 0.0) {



552    rtDW->throttle_avg_max = 0.0;



553  }



554



555  if (cos_tilt > 1.0) {



556    rtDW->throttle_avg_max = 1.0;



557  }



558}



559



560real_T rt_atan2d_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



561{



562  real_T y;



563  int32_T u0_0;



564  int32_T u1_0;



565  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1)) {



566    y = (rtNaN);



567  } else if (rtIsInf(u0) && rtIsInf(u1)) {



568    if (u0 > 0.0) {



569      u0_0 = 1;



570    } else {



571      u0_0 = -1;



572    }



573



574    if (u1 > 0.0) {



575      u1_0 = 1;



576    } else {



577      u1_0 = -1;



578    }



579



580    y = atan2(u0_0, u1_0);



581  } else if (u1 == 0.0) {



582    if (u0 > 0.0) {



583      y = RT_PI / 2.0;



584    } else if (u0 < 0.0) {



585      y = -(RT_PI / 2.0);



586    } else {



587      y = 0.0;



588    }



589  } else {



590    y = atan2(u0, u1);



591  }



592



593  return y;



594}

596/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



597static real_T wrap_PI(real_T radian)



598{



599  real_T res;



600  boolean_T rEQ0;



601  real_T q;



602  if (rtIsNaN(radian)) {



603    res = (rtNaN);



604  } else if (rtIsInf(radian)) {



605    res = (rtNaN);



606  } else if (radian == 0.0) {



607    res = 0.0;



608  } else {



609    res = fmod(radian, 6.2831853071795862);



610    rEQ0 = (res == 0.0);



611    if (!rEQ0) {



612      q = fabs(radian / 6.2831853071795862);



613      rEQ0 = !(fabs(q - floor(q + 0.5)) > 2.2204460492503131E-16 * q);



614    }



615



616    if (rEQ0) {



617      res = 0.0;



618    } else {



619      if (radian < 0.0) {



620        res += 6.2831853071795862;



621      }



622    }



623  }



624



625  if (res > 3.1415926535897931) {



626    res -= 6.2831853071795862;



627  }



628



629  return res;



630}

632/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



633static real_T sqrt_controller(real_T error, real_T p, real_T second_ord_lim,



634  real_T b_dt)



635{



636  real_T correction_rate;



637  real_T linear_dist;



638  real_T low;



639  real_T low_tmp;



640  if (second_ord_lim <= 0.0) {



641    correction_rate = error * p;



642  } else if (p == 0.0) {



643    if (error > 0.0) {



644      correction_rate = sqrt(2.0 * second_ord_lim * error);



645    } else if (error < 0.0) {



646      correction_rate = -sqrt(2.0 * second_ord_lim * -error);



647    } else {



648      correction_rate = 0.0;



649    }



650  } else {



651    linear_dist = second_ord_lim / p / p;



652    if (error > linear_dist) {



653      correction_rate = sqrt((error - linear_dist / 2.0) * (2.0 * second_ord_lim));



654    } else if (error < -linear_dist) {



655      correction_rate = -sqrt((-error - linear_dist / 2.0) * (2.0 *



656        second_ord_lim));



657    } else {



658      correction_rate = error * p;



659    }



660  }



661



662  linear_dist = correction_rate;



663  low_tmp = fabs(error);



664  low = -low_tmp / b_dt;



665  low_tmp /= b_dt;



666  if (correction_rate < low) {



667    correction_rate = low;



668  }



669



670  if (linear_dist > low_tmp) {



671    correction_rate = low_tmp;



672  }



673



674  return correction_rate;



675}

677/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



678static real_T norm(const real_T x[2])



679{



680  real_T y;



681  real_T scale;



682  real_T absxk;



683  real_T t;



684  scale = 3.3121686421112381E-170;



685  absxk = fabs(x[0]);



686  if (absxk > 3.3121686421112381E-170) {



687    y = 1.0;



688    scale = absxk;



689  } else {



690    t = absxk / 3.3121686421112381E-170;



691    y = t * t;



692  }



693



694  absxk = fabs(x[1]);



695  if (absxk > scale) {



696    t = scale / absxk;



697    y = y * t * t + 1.0;



698    scale = absxk;



699  } else {



700    t = absxk / scale;



701    y += t * t;



702  }



703



704  return scale * sqrt(y);



705}

707/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



708static void ang_vel_limit(const real_T euler_radin[3], real_T b_ang_vel_roll_max,



709  real_T b_ang_vel_pitch_max, real_T b_ang_vel_yaw_max, real_T euler_rado[3])



710{



711  real_T thrust_vector_ang_vel_x;



712  real_T thrust_vector_ang_vel_y;



713  real_T thrust_vector_length;



714  real_T thrust_vector_ang_vel_x_0[2];



715  euler_rado[0] = euler_radin[0];



716  euler_rado[1] = euler_radin[1];



717  euler_rado[2] = euler_radin[2];



718  if ((b_ang_vel_roll_max == 0.0) || (b_ang_vel_pitch_max == 0.0)) {



719    if (b_ang_vel_roll_max != 0.0) {



720      euler_rado[0] = euler_radin[0];



721      if (euler_radin[0] < -b_ang_vel_roll_max) {



722        euler_rado[0] = -b_ang_vel_roll_max;



723      }



724



725      if (euler_radin[0] > b_ang_vel_roll_max) {



726        euler_rado[0] = b_ang_vel_roll_max;



727      }



728    }



729



730    if (b_ang_vel_pitch_max != 0.0) {



731      euler_rado[1] = euler_radin[1];



732      if (euler_radin[1] < -b_ang_vel_pitch_max) {



733        euler_rado[1] = -b_ang_vel_pitch_max;



734      }



735



736      if (euler_radin[1] > b_ang_vel_pitch_max) {



737        euler_rado[1] = b_ang_vel_pitch_max;



738      }



739    }



740  } else {



741    thrust_vector_ang_vel_x = euler_radin[0] / b_ang_vel_roll_max;



742    thrust_vector_ang_vel_y = euler_radin[1] / b_ang_vel_pitch_max;



743    thrust_vector_ang_vel_x_0[0] = thrust_vector_ang_vel_x;



744    thrust_vector_ang_vel_x_0[1] = thrust_vector_ang_vel_y;



745    thrust_vector_length = norm(thrust_vector_ang_vel_x_0);



746    if (thrust_vector_length > 1.0) {



747      euler_rado[0] = thrust_vector_ang_vel_x * b_ang_vel_roll_max /



748        thrust_vector_length;



749      euler_rado[1] = thrust_vector_ang_vel_y * b_ang_vel_pitch_max /



750        thrust_vector_length;



751    }



752



753    if (b_ang_vel_yaw_max != 0.0) {



754      euler_rado[2] = euler_radin[2];



755      if (euler_radin[2] < -b_ang_vel_yaw_max) {



756        euler_rado[2] = -b_ang_vel_yaw_max;



757      }



758



759      if (euler_radin[2] > b_ang_vel_yaw_max) {



760        euler_rado[2] = b_ang_vel_yaw_max;



761      }



762    }



763  }



764}

766/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



767static real_T norm_p(const real_T x[3])



768{



769  real_T y;



770  real_T scale;



771  real_T absxk;



772  real_T t;



773  scale = 3.3121686421112381E-170;



774  absxk = fabs(x[0]);



775  if (absxk > 3.3121686421112381E-170) {



776    y = 1.0;



777    scale = absxk;



778  } else {



779    t = absxk / 3.3121686421112381E-170;



780    y = t * t;



781  }



782



783  absxk = fabs(x[1]);



784  if (absxk > scale) {



785    t = scale / absxk;



786    y = y * t * t + 1.0;



787    scale = absxk;



788  } else {



789    t = absxk / scale;



790    y += t * t;



791  }



792



793  absxk = fabs(x[2]);



794  if (absxk > scale) {



795    t = scale / absxk;



796    y = y * t * t + 1.0;



797    scale = absxk;



798  } else {



799    t = absxk / scale;



800    y += t * t;



801  }



802



803  return scale * sqrt(y);



804}

806/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



807static void from_axis_angle(const real_T axisin[3], real_T theta, real_T q[4])



808{



809  real_T st2;



810  if (theta == 0.0) {



811    q[0] = 1.0;



812    q[1] = 0.0;



813    q[2] = 0.0;



814    q[3] = 0.0;



815  } else {



816    st2 = sin(theta / 2.0);



817    q[0] = cos(theta / 2.0);



818    q[1] = axisin[0] * st2;



819    q[2] = axisin[1] * st2;



820    q[3] = axisin[2] * st2;



821  }



822}

824/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



825static void quatmultiply(const real_T q[4], const real_T r[4], real_T qout[4])



826{



827  qout[0] = ((q[0] * r[0] - q[1] * r[1]) - q[2] * r[2]) - q[3] * r[3];



828  qout[1] = (q[0] * r[1] + r[0] * q[1]) + (q[2] * r[3] - q[3] * r[2]);



829  qout[2] = (q[0] * r[2] + r[0] * q[2]) + (q[3] * r[1] - q[1] * r[3]);



830  qout[3] = (q[0] * r[3] + r[0] * q[3]) + (q[1] * r[2] - q[2] * r[1]);



831}

833/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



834static void normalizeq(real_T q[4])



835{



836  real_T quatMag;



837  real_T scale;



838  real_T absxk;



839  real_T t;



840  scale = 3.3121686421112381E-170;



841  absxk = fabs(q[0]);



842  if (absxk > 3.3121686421112381E-170) {



843    quatMag = 1.0;



844    scale = absxk;



845  } else {



846    t = absxk / 3.3121686421112381E-170;



847    quatMag = t * t;



848  }



849



850  absxk = fabs(q[1]);



851  if (absxk > scale) {



852    t = scale / absxk;



853    quatMag = quatMag * t * t + 1.0;



854    scale = absxk;



855  } else {



856    t = absxk / scale;



857    quatMag += t * t;



858  }



859



860  absxk = fabs(q[2]);



861  if (absxk > scale) {



862    t = scale / absxk;



863    quatMag = quatMag * t * t + 1.0;



864    scale = absxk;



865  } else {



866    t = absxk / scale;



867    quatMag += t * t;



868  }



869



870  absxk = fabs(q[3]);



871  if (absxk > scale) {



872    t = scale / absxk;



873    quatMag = quatMag * t * t + 1.0;



874    scale = absxk;



875  } else {



876    t = absxk / scale;



877    quatMag += t * t;



878  }



879



880  quatMag = scale * sqrt(quatMag);



881  if (quatMag != 0.0) {



882    q[0] /= quatMag;



883    q[1] /= quatMag;



884    q[2] /= quatMag;



885    q[3] /= quatMag;



886  }



887}

889/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



890static void attitude_controller_run_quat(const real_T attitude_target_ang_vel[3],



891  DW *rtDW)



892{



893  real_T attitude_vehicle_quat[4];



894  real_T feedforward_scalar;



895  real_T att_to_thrust_vec[3];



896  real_T thrust_vec_cross[3];



897  real_T thrust_vector_length;



898  real_T thrust_vec_correction_quat[4];



899  real_T yaw_vec_correction_quat[4];



900  real_T att_diff_angle_y;



901  real_T q[4];



902  real_T b_l;



903  real_T low;



904  real_T b_theta;



905  real_T att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[3];



906  real_T tmp[9];



907  int32_T i;



908  real_T high;



909  real_T tmp_0[4];



910  from_rotation_matrix(rtDW->rot_body_to_ned, attitude_vehicle_quat);



911  rotation_matrix(rtDW->attitude_target_quat, tmp);



912  for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {



913    att_to_thrust_vec[i] = tmp[i + 6] + (tmp[i + 3] * 0.0 + tmp[i] * 0.0);



914  }



915



916  rotation_matrix(attitude_vehicle_quat, tmp);



917  feedforward_scalar = 0.0;



918  for (i = 0; i < 3; i++) {



919    thrust_vector_length = tmp[i + 6] + (tmp[i + 3] * 0.0 + tmp[i] * 0.0);



920    feedforward_scalar += thrust_vector_length * att_to_thrust_vec[i];



921    att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[i] = thrust_vector_length;



922  }



923



924  thrust_vec_cross[0] = att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[1] * att_to_thrust_vec[2] -



925    att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[2] * att_to_thrust_vec[1];



926  thrust_vec_cross[1] = att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[2] * att_to_thrust_vec[0] -



927    att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[0] * att_to_thrust_vec[2];



928  thrust_vec_cross[2] = att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[0] * att_to_thrust_vec[1] -



929    att_from_thrust_vec_tmp[1] * att_to_thrust_vec[0];



930  thrust_vector_length = feedforward_scalar;



931  if (feedforward_scalar < -1.0) {



932    thrust_vector_length = -1.0;



933  }



934



935  if (feedforward_scalar > 1.0) {



936    thrust_vector_length = 1.0;



937  }



938



939  feedforward_scalar = acos(thrust_vector_length);



940  thrust_vector_length = norm_p(thrust_vec_cross);



941  if ((thrust_vector_length == 0.0) || (feedforward_scalar == 0.0)) {



942    thrust_vec_cross[0] = 0.0;



943    thrust_vec_cross[1] = 0.0;



944    thrust_vec_cross[2] = 1.0;



945    feedforward_scalar = 0.0;



946  } else {



947    thrust_vec_cross[0] /= thrust_vector_length;



948    thrust_vec_cross[1] /= thrust_vector_length;



949    thrust_vec_cross[2] /= thrust_vector_length;



950  }



951



952  q[0] = attitude_vehicle_quat[0];



953  q[1] = -attitude_vehicle_quat[1];



954  q[2] = -attitude_vehicle_quat[2];



955  q[3] = -attitude_vehicle_quat[3];



956  from_axis_angle(thrust_vec_cross, feedforward_scalar, tmp_0);



957  quatmultiply(q, tmp_0, yaw_vec_correction_quat);



958  quatmultiply(yaw_vec_correction_quat, attitude_vehicle_quat,



959               thrust_vec_correction_quat);



960  q[0] = thrust_vec_correction_quat[0];



961  q[1] = -thrust_vec_correction_quat[1];



962  q[2] = -thrust_vec_correction_quat[2];



963  q[3] = -thrust_vec_correction_quat[3];



964  yaw_vec_correction_quat[0] = attitude_vehicle_quat[0];



965  yaw_vec_correction_quat[1] = -attitude_vehicle_quat[1];



966  yaw_vec_correction_quat[2] = -attitude_vehicle_quat[2];



967  yaw_vec_correction_quat[3] = -attitude_vehicle_quat[3];



968  quatmultiply(q, yaw_vec_correction_quat, tmp_0);



969  quatmultiply(tmp_0, rtDW->attitude_target_quat, yaw_vec_correction_quat);



970  thrust_vector_length = sqrt((thrust_vec_correction_quat[1] *



971    thrust_vec_correction_quat[1] + thrust_vec_correction_quat[2] *



972    thrust_vec_correction_quat[2]) + thrust_vec_correction_quat[3] *



973    thrust_vec_correction_quat[3]);



974  att_to_thrust_vec[0] = thrust_vec_correction_quat[1];



975  att_to_thrust_vec[1] = thrust_vec_correction_quat[2];



976  if (thrust_vector_length != 0.0) {



977    att_to_thrust_vec[0] = thrust_vec_correction_quat[1] / thrust_vector_length;



978    att_to_thrust_vec[1] = thrust_vec_correction_quat[2] / thrust_vector_length;



979    thrust_vector_length = wrap_PI(2.0 * rt_atan2d_snf(thrust_vector_length,



980      thrust_vec_correction_quat[0]));



981    att_to_thrust_vec[0] *= thrust_vector_length;



982    att_to_thrust_vec[1] *= thrust_vector_length;



983  }



984



985  thrust_vector_length = att_to_thrust_vec[0];



986  att_diff_angle_y = att_to_thrust_vec[1];



987  b_l = sqrt((yaw_vec_correction_quat[1] * yaw_vec_correction_quat[1] +



988              yaw_vec_correction_quat[2] * yaw_vec_correction_quat[2]) +



989             yaw_vec_correction_quat[3] * yaw_vec_correction_quat[3]);



990  att_to_thrust_vec[2] = yaw_vec_correction_quat[3];



991  if (b_l != 0.0) {



992    att_to_thrust_vec[2] = yaw_vec_correction_quat[3] / b_l;



993    b_l = wrap_PI(2.0 * rt_atan2d_snf(b_l, yaw_vec_correction_quat[0]));



994    att_to_thrust_vec[2] *= b_l;



995  }



996



997  b_l = att_to_thrust_vec[2];



998  if (rtDW->p_angle_yaw != 0.0) {



999    high = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_Y_CONTROLLER_ / rtDW->p_angle_yaw;



1000    if (fabs(att_to_thrust_vec[2]) > high) {



1001      b_theta = wrap_PI(att_to_thrust_vec[2]);



1002      low = -rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_Y_CONTROLLER_ / rtDW->p_angle_yaw;



1003      b_l = b_theta;



1004      if (b_theta < low) {



1005        b_l = low;



1006      }



1007



1008      if (b_theta > high) {



1009        b_l = high;



1010      }



1011



1012      att_to_thrust_vec[0] = 0.0;



1013      att_to_thrust_vec[1] = 0.0;



1014      att_to_thrust_vec[2] = b_l;



1015      b_theta = norm_p(att_to_thrust_vec);



1016      if (b_theta == 0.0) {



1017        yaw_vec_correction_quat[0] = 1.0;



1018        yaw_vec_correction_quat[1] = 0.0;



1019        yaw_vec_correction_quat[2] = 0.0;



1020        yaw_vec_correction_quat[3] = 0.0;



1021      } else {



1022        att_to_thrust_vec[0] = 0.0 / b_theta;



1023        att_to_thrust_vec[1] = 0.0 / b_theta;



1024        att_to_thrust_vec[2] = b_l / b_theta;



1025        from_axis_angle(att_to_thrust_vec, b_theta, yaw_vec_correction_quat);



1026      }



1027



1028      quatmultiply(attitude_vehicle_quat, thrust_vec_correction_quat, tmp_0);



1029      quatmultiply(tmp_0, yaw_vec_correction_quat, rtDW->attitude_target_quat);



1030    }



1031  }



1032



1033  att_to_thrust_vec[0] = thrust_vector_length;



1034  att_to_thrust_vec[1] = att_diff_angle_y;



1035  att_to_thrust_vec[2] = b_l;



1036  if (rtDW->use_sqrt_controller != 0.0) {



1037    thrust_vector_length = rtDW->accel_roll_max * 0.01 / 2.0;



1038    att_diff_angle_y = thrust_vector_length;



1039    if (thrust_vector_length < rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLL_j) {



1040      att_diff_angle_y = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLL_j;



1041    }



1042



1043    if (thrust_vector_length > rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLLER) {



1044      att_diff_angle_y = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLLER;



1045    }



1046



1047    rtDW->rate_target_ang_vel[0] = sqrt_controller(att_to_thrust_vec[0],



1048      rtDW->p_angle_roll, att_diff_angle_y, rtDW->dt);



1049    att_diff_angle_y = rtDW->accel_pitch_max * 0.01 / 2.0;



1050    b_l = att_diff_angle_y;



1051    if (att_diff_angle_y < rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLL_j) {



1052      b_l = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLL_j;



1053    }



1054



1055    if (att_diff_angle_y > rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLLER) {



1056      b_l = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_RP_CONTROLLER;



1057    }



1058



1059    rtDW->rate_target_ang_vel[1] = sqrt_controller(att_to_thrust_vec[1],



1060      rtDW->p_angle_pitch, b_l, rtDW->dt);



1061    b_l = rtDW->accel_yaw_max * 0.01 / 2.0;



1062    b_theta = b_l;



1063    if (b_l < rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_Y_CONTROLLE_g) {



1064      b_theta = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_Y_CONTROLLE_g;



1065    }



1066



1067    if (b_l > rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_Y_CONTROLLER_) {



1068      b_theta = rtDW->AC_ATTITUDE_ACCEL_Y_CONTROLLER_;



1069    }



1070



1071    rtDW->rate_target_ang_vel[2] = sqrt_controller(att_to_thrust_vec[2],

1165  } else {



1166    normalizeq(rtDW->attitude_target_quat);



1167  }



1168}

1451    } else {



1452      if (rtDW->rate_yaw_pid_integrator > rtDW->ATC_RAT_YAW_IMAX) {



1453        rtDW->rate_yaw_pid_integrator = rtDW->ATC_RAT_YAW_IMAX;



1454      }



1455    }



1456  }



1457



1458  rtDW->yaw_in = ((rtDW->ATC_RAT_YAW_P * rtDW->rate_yaw_pid_input +



1459                   rtDW->rate_yaw_pid_integrator) + rtDW->ATC_RAT_YAW_D *



1460                  rtDW->rate_yaw_pid_derivative) + rtDW->ATC_RAT_YAW_FF *



1461    rtDW->rate_target_ang_vel[2];



1462}

1464/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



1465static void update_throttle_filter(DW *rtDW)



1466{



1467  real_T throttle_filter_temp;



1468  real_T alpha;



1469  real_T thrust_dt;



1470  real_T amt;



1471  if (rtDW->armed != 0.0) {



1472    throttle_filter_temp = rtDW->throttle_filter;



1473    if (rtDW->throttle_cutoff_frequency <= 0.0) {



1474      rtDW->throttle_filter = rtDW->throttle_in;



1475    }



1476



1477    amt = rtDW->dt / (1.0 / (6.2831853071795862 *



1478      rtDW->throttle_cutoff_frequency) + rtDW->dt);



1479    alpha = amt;



1480    if (amt < 0.0) {



1481      alpha = 0.0;



1482    }



1483



1484    if (amt > 1.0) {



1485      alpha = 1.0;



1486    }



1487



1488    rtDW->throttle_filter += (rtDW->throttle_in - rtDW->throttle_filter) * alpha;



1489    if (rtDW->throttle_filter < 0.0) {



1490      rtDW->throttle_filter = 0.0;



1491    }



1492



1493    if (rtDW->throttle_filter > 1.0) {



1494      rtDW->throttle_filter = 1.0;



1495    }



1496



1497    thrust_dt = rtDW->dt / rtDW->thrust_slew_time / 3.0;



1498    amt = rtDW->throttle_filter;



1499    alpha = throttle_filter_temp - thrust_dt;



1500    throttle_filter_temp += thrust_dt;



1501    if (rtDW->throttle_filter < alpha) {



1502      rtDW->throttle_filter = alpha;



1503    }



1504



1505    if (amt > throttle_filter_temp) {



1506      rtDW->throttle_filter = throttle_filter_temp;



1507    }



1508



1509    if (rtDW->throttle_filter > 0.9) {



1510      rtDW->throttle_filter = 0.9;



1511    }



1512  } else {



1513    rtDW->throttle_filter = 0.0;



1514  }



1515}

1517/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



1518static void output_armed_stabilizing(DW *rtDW)



1519{



1520  real_T rpy_scale;



1521  real_T compensation_gain;



1522  real_T roll_thrust;



1523  real_T pitch_thrust;



1524  real_T yaw_thrust;



1525  real_T throttle_thrust;



1526  real_T rp_low;



1527  real_T rp_high;



1528  rpy_scale = 1.0;



1529  compensation_gain = 1.0;



1530  if ((rtDW->air_density_ratio > 0.3) && (rtDW->air_density_ratio < 1.5)) {



1531    yaw_thrust = rtDW->air_density_ratio;



1532    if (rtDW->air_density_ratio < 0.5) {



1533      yaw_thrust = 0.5;



1534    }



1535



1536    if (rtDW->air_density_ratio > 1.25) {



1537      yaw_thrust = 1.25;



1538    }



1539



1540    compensation_gain = 1.0 / yaw_thrust;



1541  }



1542



1543  roll_thrust = rtDW->roll_in * compensation_gain;



1544  pitch_thrust = rtDW->pitch_in * compensation_gain;



1545  yaw_thrust = rtDW->yaw_in * compensation_gain;



1546  throttle_thrust = rtDW->throttle_filter * compensation_gain;



1547  compensation_gain *= rtDW->throttle_avg_max;



1548  rtDW->throttle_thrust_max = (1.0 - rtDW->thrust_boost_ratio) *



1549    rtDW->throttle_thrust_max + rtDW->thrust_boost_ratio;



1550  rtDW->throttle_lower = 0.0;



1551  if (throttle_thrust <= 0.0) {



1552    throttle_thrust = 0.0;



1553    rtDW->throttle_lower = 1.0;



1554  }



1555



1556  rtDW->throttle_upper = 0.0;



1557  if (throttle_thrust >= rtDW->throttle_thrust_max) {



1558    throttle_thrust = rtDW->throttle_thrust_max;



1559    rtDW->throttle_upper = 1.0;



1560  }



1561



1562  rp_low = compensation_gain;



1563  if (compensation_gain < throttle_thrust) {



1564    compensation_gain = throttle_thrust;



1565  }



1566



1567  if (rp_low > rtDW->throttle_thrust_max) {



1568    compensation_gain = rtDW->throttle_thrust_max;



1569  }



1570



1571  rp_low = 1.0;



1572  rp_high = -1.0;



1573  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] = (fabs(rtDW->pitch_factor[0]) * rtDW->Kx * 0.0 +



1574    rtDW->pitch_factor[0]) * pitch_thrust + roll_thrust * rtDW->roll_factor[0];



1575  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] < 1.0) {



1576    rp_low = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0];



1577  }



1578



1579  if ((rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] > -1.0) && (!(rtDW->thrust_boost != 0.0))) {



1580    rp_high = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0];



1581  }



1582



1583  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] = (fabs(rtDW->pitch_factor[1]) * rtDW->Kx * 0.0 +



1584    rtDW->pitch_factor[1]) * pitch_thrust + roll_thrust * rtDW->roll_factor[1];



1585  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] < rp_low) {



1586    rp_low = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1];



1587  }



1588



1589  if ((rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] > rp_high) && (!(rtDW->thrust_boost != 0.0))) {



1590    rp_high = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1];



1591  }



1592



1593  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] = (fabs(rtDW->pitch_factor[2]) * rtDW->Kx * 0.0 +



1594    rtDW->pitch_factor[2]) * pitch_thrust + roll_thrust * rtDW->roll_factor[2];



1595  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] < rp_low) {



1596    rp_low = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2];



1597  }



1598



1599  if ((rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] > rp_high) && (!(rtDW->thrust_boost != 0.0))) {



1600    rp_high = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2];



1601  }



1602



1603  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] = (fabs(rtDW->pitch_factor[3]) * rtDW->Kx * 0.0 +



1604    rtDW->pitch_factor[3]) * pitch_thrust + roll_thrust * rtDW->roll_factor[3];



1605  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] < rp_low) {



1606    rp_low = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3];



1607  }



1608



1609  if ((rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] > rp_high) && (!(rtDW->thrust_boost != 0.0))) {



1610    rp_high = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3];



1611  }



1612



1613  roll_thrust = fmin(0.5, compensation_gain);



1614  roll_thrust = fmax(fmin(roll_thrust + rp_low, 1.0 - (roll_thrust + rp_high)),



1615                     (1.0 - rtDW->thrust_boost_ratio) * (rtDW->yaw_headroom /



1616    1000.0) + rtDW->thrust_boost_ratio * 0.5) / 2.5599;



1617  if (fabs(yaw_thrust) > roll_thrust) {



1618    pitch_thrust = yaw_thrust;



1619    if (yaw_thrust < -roll_thrust) {



1620      yaw_thrust = -roll_thrust;



1621    }



1622



1623    if (pitch_thrust > roll_thrust) {



1624      yaw_thrust = roll_thrust;



1625    }



1626  }



1627



1628  roll_thrust = 1.0;



1629  pitch_thrust = -1.0;



1630  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] += yaw_thrust * rtDW->yaw_factor[0];



1631  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] < 1.0) {



1632    roll_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0];



1633  }



1634



1635  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] > -1.0) {



1636    pitch_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0];



1637  }



1638



1639  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] += yaw_thrust * rtDW->yaw_factor[1];



1640  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] < roll_thrust) {



1641    roll_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1];



1642  }



1643



1644  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] > pitch_thrust) {



1645    pitch_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1];



1646  }



1647



1648  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] += yaw_thrust * rtDW->yaw_factor[2];



1649  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] < roll_thrust) {



1650    roll_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2];



1651  }



1652



1653  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] > pitch_thrust) {



1654    pitch_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2];



1655  }



1656



1657  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] += yaw_thrust * rtDW->yaw_factor[3];



1658  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] < roll_thrust) {



1659    roll_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3];



1660  }



1661



1662  if (rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] > pitch_thrust) {



1663    pitch_thrust = rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3];



1664  }



1665



1666  rp_low = pitch_thrust - roll_thrust;



1667  if (rp_low > 1.0) {



1668    rpy_scale = 1.0 / rp_low;



1669  }



1670



1671  if (roll_thrust < 0.0) {



1672    rpy_scale = fmin(rpy_scale, -compensation_gain / roll_thrust);



1673  }



1674



1675  pitch_thrust *= rpy_scale;



1676  roll_thrust *= rpy_scale;



1677  yaw_thrust = throttle_thrust - (-roll_thrust);



1678  if (rpy_scale < 1.0) {



1679    if (yaw_thrust > 0.0) {



1680      rtDW->throttle_upper = 1.0;



1681    }



1682



1683    yaw_thrust = 0.0;



1684  } else if (yaw_thrust < 0.0) {



1685    yaw_thrust = 0.0;



1686  } else {



1687    rp_low = 1.0 - (-roll_thrust + pitch_thrust);



1688    if (yaw_thrust > rp_low) {



1689      yaw_thrust = rp_low;



1690      rtDW->throttle_upper = 1.0;



1691    }



1692  }



1693



1694  compensation_gain = -roll_thrust + yaw_thrust;



1695  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] = compensation_gain + rpy_scale *



1696    rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0];



1697  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] = compensation_gain + rpy_scale *



1698    rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1];



1699  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] = compensation_gain + rpy_scale *



1700    rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2];



1701  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] = compensation_gain + rpy_scale *



1702    rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3];



1703  rpy_scale = cos(rtDW->current_tilt);



1704  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] *= rpy_scale;



1705  rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] *= rpy_scale;



1706}

1708/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



1709static void AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(DW *rtDW)



1710{



1711  real_T thrust_dt;



1712  real_T pwm_out_temp;



1713  real_T low;



1714  real_T high;



1715  real_T thrust_dt_tmp;



1716  update_throttle_filter(rtDW);



1717  output_armed_stabilizing(rtDW);



1718  thrust_dt_tmp = rtDW->pwm_max - rtDW->pwm_min;



1719  thrust_dt = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->dt / rtDW->thrust_slew_time;



1720  pwm_out_temp = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->k_throttle + rtDW->pwm_min;



1721  low = rtDW->pwm_tail - thrust_dt;



1722  high = rtDW->pwm_tail + thrust_dt;



1723  rtDW->pwm_tail = pwm_out_temp;



1724  if (pwm_out_temp < low) {



1725    rtDW->pwm_tail = low;



1726  }



1727



1728  if (pwm_out_temp > high) {



1729    rtDW->pwm_tail = high;



1730  }



1731



1732  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_tail;



1733  if (rtDW->pwm_tail < rtDW->pwm_min) {



1734    rtDW->pwm_tail = rtDW->pwm_min;



1735  }



1736



1737  if (pwm_out_temp > rtDW->pwm_max) {



1738    rtDW->pwm_tail = rtDW->pwm_max;



1739  }



1740



1741  pwm_out_temp = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[0] + rtDW->pwm_min;



1742  low = rtDW->pwm_out[0] - thrust_dt;



1743  high = rtDW->pwm_out[0] + thrust_dt;



1744  rtDW->pwm_out[0] = pwm_out_temp;



1745  if (pwm_out_temp < low) {



1746    rtDW->pwm_out[0] = low;



1747  }



1748



1749  if (pwm_out_temp > high) {



1750    rtDW->pwm_out[0] = high;



1751  }



1752



1753  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[0];



1754  if (rtDW->pwm_out[0] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



1755    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



1756  }



1757



1758  if (rtDW->pwm_out[0] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



1759    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



1760  }



1761



1762  rtDW->pwm_out[0] = pwm_out_temp;



1763  pwm_out_temp = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[1] + rtDW->pwm_min;



1764  low = rtDW->pwm_out[1] - thrust_dt;



1765  high = rtDW->pwm_out[1] + thrust_dt;



1766  rtDW->pwm_out[1] = pwm_out_temp;



1767  if (pwm_out_temp < low) {



1768    rtDW->pwm_out[1] = low;



1769  }



1770



1771  if (pwm_out_temp > high) {



1772    rtDW->pwm_out[1] = high;



1773  }



1774



1775  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[1];



1776  if (rtDW->pwm_out[1] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



1777    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



1778  }



1779



1780  if (rtDW->pwm_out[1] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



1781    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



1782  }



1783



1784  rtDW->pwm_out[1] = pwm_out_temp;



1785  pwm_out_temp = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[2] + rtDW->pwm_min;



1786  low = rtDW->pwm_out[2] - thrust_dt;



1787  high = rtDW->pwm_out[2] + thrust_dt;



1788  rtDW->pwm_out[2] = pwm_out_temp;



1789  if (pwm_out_temp < low) {



1790    rtDW->pwm_out[2] = low;



1791  }



1792



1793  if (pwm_out_temp > high) {



1794    rtDW->pwm_out[2] = high;



1795  }



1796



1797  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[2];



1798  if (rtDW->pwm_out[2] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



1799    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



1800  }



1801



1802  if (rtDW->pwm_out[2] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



1803    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



1804  }



1805



1806  rtDW->pwm_out[2] = pwm_out_temp;



1807  pwm_out_temp = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->thrust_rpyt_out[3] + rtDW->pwm_min;



1808  low = rtDW->pwm_out[3] - thrust_dt;



1809  high = rtDW->pwm_out[3] + thrust_dt;



1810  rtDW->pwm_out[3] = pwm_out_temp;



1811  if (pwm_out_temp < low) {



1812    rtDW->pwm_out[3] = low;



1813  }



1814



1815  if (pwm_out_temp > high) {



1816    rtDW->pwm_out[3] = high;



1817  }



1818



1819  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[3];



1820  if (rtDW->pwm_out[3] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



1821    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



1822  }



1823



1824  if (rtDW->pwm_out[3] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



1825    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



1826  }



1827



1828  rtDW->pwm_out[3] = pwm_out_temp;



1829}

1831/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



1832static void set_alt_target_from_climb_rate_(real_T b_climb_rate_cms, real_T b_dt,



1833  real_T force_descend, DW *rtDW)



1834{



1835  real_T accel_z_cms;



1836  real_T jerk_z;



1837  accel_z_cms = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z;



1838  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] < rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN) &&



1839      (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN != 0.0)) {



1840    accel_z_cms = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z * rtDW->POSCONTROL_OVERSPEED_GAIN_Z *



1841      rtDW->vel_desired[2] / rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN;



1842  }



1843



1844  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] > rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP) &&



1845      (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP != 0.0)) {



1846    accel_z_cms = accel_z_cms * rtDW->POSCONTROL_OVERSPEED_GAIN_Z *



1847      rtDW->vel_desired[2] / rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP;



1848  }



1849



1850  jerk_z = accel_z_cms;



1851  if (accel_z_cms < 0.0) {



1852    accel_z_cms = 0.0;



1853  }



1854



1855  if (jerk_z > 750.0) {



1856    accel_z_cms = 750.0;



1857  }



1858



1859  jerk_z = accel_z_cms * rtDW->POSCONTROL_JERK_RATIO;



1860  rtDW->accel_last_z_cms += jerk_z * b_dt;



1861  rtDW->accel_last_z_cms = fmin(fmin(accel_z_cms, sqrt(fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[2]



1862    - b_climb_rate_cms) * 2.0 * jerk_z)), rtDW->accel_last_z_cms);



1863  jerk_z = rtDW->accel_last_z_cms * b_dt;



1864  accel_z_cms = rtDW->vel_desired[2] - jerk_z;



1865  jerk_z += rtDW->vel_desired[2];



1866  rtDW->vel_desired[2] = b_climb_rate_cms;



1867  if (b_climb_rate_cms < accel_z_cms) {



1868    rtDW->vel_desired[2] = accel_z_cms;



1869  }



1870



1871  if (b_climb_rate_cms > jerk_z) {



1872    rtDW->vel_desired[2] = jerk_z;



1873  }



1874



1875  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] < 0.0) && ((!(rtDW->throttle_lower != 0.0)) ||



1876       (force_descend != 0.0))) {



1877    rtDW->pos_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2] * b_dt;



1878  } else {



1879    if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] > 0.0) && ((!(rtDW->throttle_upper != 0.0)) &&



1880         (!(rtDW->limit_pos_up != 0.0)))) {



1881      rtDW->pos_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2] * b_dt;



1882    }



1883  }



1884}

1886/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



1887static void update_z_controller(DW *rtDW)



1888{



1889  real_T alpha;



1890  real_T i;



1891  if (rtDW->recalc_leash_z != 0.0) {



1892    alpha = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z;



1893    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z <= 0.0) {



1894      alpha = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCELERATION_MIN;



1895    }



1896



1897    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P <= 0.0) {



1898      rtDW->leash_up_z = rtDW->POSCONTROL_LEASH_LENGTH_MIN;



1899    } else {



1900      if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP <= alpha / rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P) {



1901        rtDW->leash_up_z = rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP / rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P;



1902      } else {



1903        rtDW->leash_up_z = alpha / (2.0 * rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P *



1904          rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P) + rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP *



1905          rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP / (2.0 * alpha);



1906      }



1907



1908      if (rtDW->leash_up_z < rtDW->POSCONTROL_LEASH_LENGTH_MIN) {



1909        rtDW->leash_up_z = rtDW->POSCONTROL_LEASH_LENGTH_MIN;



1910      }



1911    }



1912



1913    alpha = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z;



1914    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z <= 0.0) {



1915      alpha = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCELERATION_MIN;



1916    }



1917



1918    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P <= 0.0) {



1919      rtDW->leash_down_z = rtDW->POSCONTROL_LEASH_LENGTH_MIN;



1920    } else {



1921      if (-rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN <= alpha / rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P) {



1922        rtDW->leash_down_z = -rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN /



1923          rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P;



1924      } else {



1925        rtDW->leash_down_z = alpha / (2.0 * rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P *



1926          rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P) + -rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN *



1927          -rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN / (2.0 * alpha);



1928      }



1929



1930      if (rtDW->leash_down_z < rtDW->POSCONTROL_LEASH_LENGTH_MIN) {



1931        rtDW->leash_down_z = rtDW->POSCONTROL_LEASH_LENGTH_MIN;



1932      }



1933    }



1934



1935    rtDW->recalc_leash_z = 0.0;



1936  }



1937



1938  rtDW->limit_pos_up = 0.0;



1939  rtDW->pos_error[2] = rtDW->pos_target[2] - rtDW->curr_alt;



1940  if (rtDW->pos_error[2] > rtDW->leash_up_z) {



1941    rtDW->pos_target[2] = rtDW->curr_alt + rtDW->leash_up_z;



1942    rtDW->pos_error[2] = rtDW->leash_up_z;



1943    rtDW->limit_pos_up = 1.0;



1944  }



1945



1946  if (rtDW->pos_error[2] < -rtDW->leash_down_z) {



1947    rtDW->pos_target[2] = rtDW->curr_alt - rtDW->leash_down_z;



1948    rtDW->pos_error[2] = -rtDW->leash_down_z;



1949  }



1950



1951  rtDW->vel_target[2] = sqrt_controller(rtDW->pos_error[2],



1952    rtDW->POSCONTROL_POS_Z_P, rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z, rtDW->dt);



1953  if (rtDW->vel_target[2] < rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN) {



1954    rtDW->vel_target[2] = rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN;



1955  }



1956



1957  if (rtDW->vel_target[2] > rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP) {



1958    rtDW->vel_target[2] = rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP;



1959  }



1960



1961  if (rtDW->take_off_land != 0.0) {



1962    rtDW->vel_target[2] = rtDW->vel_desired[2];



1963  } else {



1964    rtDW->vel_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2];



1965  }



1966



1967  if (rtDW->reset_rate_to_accel_z != 0.0) {



1968    rtDW->vel_error[2] = 0.0;



1969    rtDW->vel_error_input = 0.0;



1970    rtDW->reset_rate_to_accel_z = 0.0;



1971  } else {



1972    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_VEL_ERROR_CUTOFF_FRE <= 0.0) {



1973      rtDW->vel_error_input = rtDW->vel_target[2] - rtDW->curr_vel[2];



1974    } else {



1975      rtDW->vel_error_input += rtDW->dt / (1.0 / (6.2831853071795862 *



1976        rtDW->POSCONTROL_VEL_ERROR_CUTOFF_FRE) + rtDW->dt) * ((rtDW->vel_target



1977        [2] - rtDW->curr_vel[2]) - rtDW->vel_error_input);



1978    }



1979



1980    rtDW->vel_error[2] = rtDW->vel_error_input;



1981  }



1982



1983  rtDW->accel_target[2] = rtDW->POSCONTROL_VEL_Z_P * rtDW->vel_error[2];



1984  if (rtDW->pid_accel_z_reset_filter != 0.0) {



1985    rtDW->pid_accel_z_reset_filter = 0.0;



1986    rtDW->pid_accel_z_input = rtDW->accel_target[2];



1987    alpha = 0.0;



1988    rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator = 0.0;



1989  } else {



1990    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ == 0.0) {



1991      alpha = 1.0;



1992    } else {



1993      alpha = rtDW->dt / (1.0 / (6.2831853071795862 *



1994        rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ) + rtDW->dt);



1995    }



1996



1997    alpha *= rtDW->accel_target[2] - rtDW->pid_accel_z_input;



1998    rtDW->pid_accel_z_input += alpha;



1999    alpha /= rtDW->dt;



2000  }



2001



2002  i = rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator;



2003  if (((!(rtDW->throttle_lower != 0.0)) && (!(rtDW->throttle_upper != 0.0))) ||



2004      ((rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator > 0.0) && (rtDW->accel_target[2] < 0.0)) ||



2005      ((rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator < 0.0) && (rtDW->accel_target[2] > 0.0))) {



2006    if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_I != 0.0) {



2007      rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator += rtDW->pid_accel_z_input *



2008        rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_I * rtDW->dt;



2009      if (rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator < -rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_IMAX) {



2010        rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator = -rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_IMAX;



2011      } else {



2012        if (rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator > rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_IMAX) {



2013          rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_IMAX;



2014        }



2015      }



2016



2017      i = rtDW->pid_accel_z_integrator;



2018    } else {



2019      i = 0.0;



2020    }



2021  }



2022



2023  alpha = ((rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_P * rtDW->pid_accel_z_input + i) +



2024           rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_D * alpha) * 0.001 + rtDW->throttle_hover;



2025  i = alpha;



2026  if (alpha < rtDW->thr_out_min) {



2027    alpha = rtDW->thr_out_min;



2028  }



2029



2030  if (i > 1.0) {



2031    alpha = 1.0;



2032  }



2033



2034  set_throttle_out(alpha, 1.0, rtDW->POSCONTROL_THROTTLE_CUTOFF_FREQ, rtDW);



2035}

2037/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



2038static real_T get_weathervane_yaw_rate_cds(DW *rtDW)



2039{



2040  real_T weathervane_yaw_rate_cds;



2041  real_T b_roll;



2042  real_T output;



2043  b_roll = rtDW->roll_target / 100.0;



2044  if (fabs(b_roll) < rtDW->weathervane_min_roll) {



2045    rtDW->weathervane_last_output = 0.0;



2046    weathervane_yaw_rate_cds = 0.0;



2047  } else {



2048    if (b_roll > 0.0) {



2049      b_roll -= rtDW->weathervane_min_roll;



2050    } else {



2051      b_roll += rtDW->weathervane_min_roll;



2052    }



2053



2054    b_roll = b_roll / 45.0 * rtDW->weathervane_gain;



2055    output = b_roll;



2056    if (b_roll < -1.0) {



2057      output = -1.0;



2058    }



2059



2060    if (b_roll > 1.0) {



2061      output = 1.0;



2062    }



2063



2064    rtDW->weathervane_last_output = 0.98 * rtDW->weathervane_last_output + 0.02 *



2065      output;



2066    weathervane_yaw_rate_cds = rtDW->yaw_rate_max / 2.0 *



2067      rtDW->weathervane_last_output * 100.0;



2068  }



2069



2070  return weathervane_yaw_rate_cds;



2071}

2073real_T rt_remd_snf(real_T u0, real_T u1)



2074{



2075  real_T y;



2076  real_T q;



2077  if (rtIsNaN(u0) || rtIsNaN(u1) || rtIsInf(u0)) {



2078    y = (rtNaN);



2079  } else if (rtIsInf(u1)) {



2080    y = u0;



2081  } else if ((u1 != 0.0) && (u1 != trunc(u1))) {



2082    q = fabs(u0 / u1);



2083    if (!(fabs(q - floor(q + 0.5)) > DBL_EPSILON * q)) {



2084      y = 0.0 * u0;



2085    } else {



2086      y = fmod(u0, u1);



2087    }



2088  } else {



2089    y = fmod(u0, u1);



2090  }



2091



2092  return y;



2093}

2095/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



2096static void run_xy_controller(real_T b_dt, DW *rtDW)

2157  rtDW->vel_target[1] += rtDW->vel_desired[1];

2159  rtDW->vel_error[1] = rtDW->vel_target[1] - rtDW->curr_vel[1];



2160  if (rtDW->POSCONTROL_VEL_XY_FILT_HZ == 0.0) {



2161    linear_dist = 1.0;

2174  if (rtDW->pid_vel_xy_reset_filter == 1.0) {

2201        rtDW->POSCONTROL_VEL_XY_IMAX / linear_dist;



2202      rtDW->pid_vel_xy_integrator[1] = rtDW->pid_vel_xy_integrator[1] *

2216      rtDW->pid_vel_xy_integrator[1] *= linear_dist;



2217    }



2218  }



2219



2220  error_length = (rtDW->POSCONTROL_VEL_XY_P * rtDW->pid_vel_xy_input[0] +

2238    rtDW->accel_xy_input[0] += (error_length - rtDW->accel_xy_input[0]) *

2251    error_length = fabs(linear_dist);

2362/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



2363static void calc_nav_roll(DW *rtDW)



2364{



2365  real_T commanded_roll;



2366  real_T amt;



2367  commanded_roll = atan(rtDW->latAccDem * 0.101972) * cos(rtDW->pitch) * 100.0 *



2368    rtDW->HD;



2369  amt = commanded_roll;



2370  if (commanded_roll < -9000.0) {



2371    commanded_roll = -9000.0;



2372  }



2373



2374  if (amt > 9000.0) {



2375    commanded_roll = 9000.0;



2376  }



2377



2378  rtDW->nav_roll_cd = commanded_roll;



2379  if (commanded_roll < -rtDW->roll_limit_cd) {



2380    rtDW->nav_roll_cd = -rtDW->roll_limit_cd;



2381  }



2382



2383  if (commanded_roll > rtDW->roll_limit_cd) {



2384    rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_limit_cd;



2385  }



2386



2387  commanded_roll = fabs(rtDW->nav_roll_cd * 0.01);



2388  if (commanded_roll > 85.0) {



2389    commanded_roll = 85.0;



2390  }



2391



2392  rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor = 1.0 / sqrt(cos(commanded_roll / 180.0 *



2393    3.1415926535897931));



2394  rtDW->smoothed_airspeed = rtDW->smoothed_airspeed * 0.8 + rtDW->aspeed * 0.2;



2395  commanded_roll = rtDW->smoothed_airspeed / fmax(rtDW->airspeed_min, 1.0);



2396  if (commanded_roll <= 1.0) {



2397    rtDW->roll_limit_cd = 2500.0;



2398  } else if (commanded_roll < rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor) {



2399    commanded_roll = 1.0 / commanded_roll;



2400    commanded_roll = acos(commanded_roll * commanded_roll) * 100.0 * rtDW->HD;



2401    if (commanded_roll < 2500.0) {



2402      commanded_roll = 2500.0;



2403    }



2404



2405    amt = rtDW->nav_roll_cd;



2406    if (rtDW->nav_roll_cd < -commanded_roll) {



2407      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = -commanded_roll;



2408    }



2409



2410    if (amt > commanded_roll) {



2411      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = commanded_roll;



2412    }



2413



2414    rtDW->roll_limit_cd = commanded_roll;



2415  } else {



2416    commanded_roll = rtDW->nav_roll_cd;



2417    if (rtDW->nav_roll_cd < -rtDW->roll_limit_cd_inint) {



2418      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = -rtDW->roll_limit_cd_inint;



2419    }



2420



2421    if (commanded_roll > rtDW->roll_limit_cd_inint) {



2422      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_limit_cd_inint;



2423    }



2424



2425    rtDW->roll_limit_cd = rtDW->roll_limit_cd_inint;



2426  }



2427}

2866/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



2867static void update_speed(real_T load_factor, real_T *TAS_dem, real_T *TASmax,



2868  real_T *TASmin, DW *rtDW)



2869{



2870  real_T integDTAS_input;



2871  real_T integDTAS_input_tmp;



2872  *TAS_dem = rtDW->EAS_dem * rtDW->EAS2TAS;



2873  *TASmax = rtDW->airspeed_max * rtDW->EAS2TAS;



2874  *TASmin = rtDW->airspeed_min * rtDW->EAS2TAS;



2875  *TASmin *= load_factor;



2876  if (*TASmax < *TASmin) {



2877    *TASmax = *TASmin;



2878  }



2879



2880  if (*TASmin > *TAS_dem) {



2881    *TASmin = *TAS_dem;



2882  }



2883



2884  integDTAS_input_tmp = (rtDW->aspeed * rtDW->EAS2TAS - rtDW->TAS_state) *



2885    rtDW->spdCompFiltOmega;



2886  integDTAS_input = integDTAS_input_tmp * rtDW->spdCompFiltOmega;



2887  if (rtDW->TAS_state < 3.1) {



2888    integDTAS_input = fmax(integDTAS_input, 0.0);



2889  }



2890



2891  rtDW->integDTAS_state += integDTAS_input * rtDW->dt;



2892  rtDW->TAS_state += (integDTAS_input_tmp * 1.4142 + (rtDW->integDTAS_state +



2893    rtDW->vel_dot)) * rtDW->dt;



2894  rtDW->TAS_state = fmax(rtDW->TAS_state, 3.0);



2895}

3239static real_T get_bearing_to(const real_T loc2[2], const real_T b_loc[2], DW



3240  *rtDW)



3241{



3242  real_T bearing;



3243  real_T x;



3244  x = cos(b_loc[0] * 1.0E-7 / rtDW->HD);



3245  if (x < 0.01) {



3246    x = 0.01;



3247  }



3248



3249  bearing = rt_atan2d_snf(-((loc2[0] - b_loc[0]) / x), loc2[1] - b_loc[1]) *



3250    rtDW->HD * 100.0 + 9000.0;



3251  if (bearing < 0.0) {



3252    bearing += 36000.0;



3253  }



3254



3255  return bearing;



3256}

3258/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



3259static real_T prevent_indecision(real_T Nu, const real_T *target_bearing_cd, DW *



3260  rtDW)



3261{



3262  real_T Nuo;



3263  real_T yawo;



3264  if (fabs(Nu) > 2.8274333882308138) {



3265    yawo = rtDW->yaw;



3266    if (rtDW->reverse != 0.0) {



3267      yawo = wrap_PI(rtDW->yaw + 3.1415926535897931);



3268    }



3269



3270    if (fabs(wrap_PI(*target_bearing_cd / rtDW->HD / 100.0 - yawo)) > 12000.0 /



3271        rtDW->HD / 100.0) {



3272      if (rtDW->loiter_direction == 1.0) {



3273        Nu = 2.8274333882308138;



3274      } else {



3275        Nu = -2.8274333882308138;



3276      }



3277    }



3278  }



3279



3280  Nuo = Nu;



3281  if ((fabs(Nu) > 2.8274333882308138) && (fabs(rtDW->last_Nu) >



3282       2.8274333882308138)) {



3283    yawo = rtDW->yaw;



3284    if (rtDW->reverse != 0.0) {



3285      yawo = wrap_PI(rtDW->yaw + 3.1415926535897931);



3286    }



3287



3288    if ((fabs(wrap_PI(*target_bearing_cd / rtDW->HD / 100.0 - yawo)) > 12000.0 /



3289         rtDW->HD / 100.0) && (Nu * rtDW->last_Nu < 0.0)) {



3290      Nuo = rtDW->last_Nu;



3291    }



3292  }



3293



3294  return Nuo;

3298static void update_waypoint(const real_T b_prev_WP[2], const real_T b_next_WP[2],



3299  real_T b_dist_min, DW *rtDW)



3300{

3402    A_air_0 = A_air[1] / A_air_length;



3403    crosstrack_error += rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * -A_air_0;



3404    A_air_length = rt_atan2d_snf(rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * -A_air_0 -



3405      rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * AB_length, crosstrack_error);



3406    break;



3407



3408   case 1:



3409    A_air_length = cos(b_next_WP[0] * 1.0E-7 / rtDW->HD);



3410    if (A_air_length < 0.01) {



3411      A_air_length = 0.01;



3412    }



3413

3415      rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR;



3416    AB[1] = (rtDW->current_loc[1] - b_next_WP[1]) *



3417      rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR * A_air_length;



3418    A_air_length = norm(AB);



3419    AB_0 = AB[0] / A_air_length;



3420    AB_length = -AB_0;



3421    crosstrack_error = rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * -AB_0;



3422    AB_0 = AB[1] / A_air_length;



3423    crosstrack_error += rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * -AB_0;



3424    A_air_length = rt_atan2d_snf(rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * -AB_0 -



3425      rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * AB_length, crosstrack_error);



3426    break;



3427



3428   case 2:



3429    A_air_length = crosstrack_error / fmax(L1_dist, 0.1);



3430    AB_length = A_air_length;



3431    if (A_air_length < -0.7071) {



3432      A_air_length = -0.7071;



3433    }



3434



3435    if (AB_length > 0.7071) {



3436      A_air_length = 0.7071;



3437    }



3438



3439    A_air_length = asin(A_air_length);



3440    if ((rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain <= 0.0) || (rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain !=



3441         rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain_prev)) {



3442      rtDW->L1_xtrack_i = 0.0;



3443      rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain_prev = rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain;



3444    } else {



3445      if (fabs(A_air_length) < 0.087266462599716474) {



3446        rtDW->L1_xtrack_i += A_air_length * rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain * rtDW->dt;



3447        AB_length = rtDW->L1_xtrack_i;



3448        if (rtDW->L1_xtrack_i < -0.1) {



3449          rtDW->L1_xtrack_i = -0.1;



3450        }



3451



3452        if (AB_length > 0.1) {



3453          rtDW->L1_xtrack_i = 0.1;



3454        }



3455      }



3456    }



3457



3458    A_air_length += rtDW->L1_xtrack_i;



3459    A_air_length = wrap_PI(rt_atan2d_snf(rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * AB_0 -



3460      rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * AB[0], rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * AB[0] +



3461      rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * AB_0) + A_air_length);



3462    break;



3463



3464   default:



3465    A_air_length = crosstrack_error / fmax(L1_dist, 0.1);



3466    AB_length = A_air_length;



3467    if (A_air_length < -0.7071) {



3468      A_air_length = -0.7071;



3469    }



3470



3471    if (AB_length > 0.7071) {



3472      A_air_length = 0.7071;



3473    }



3474



3475    A_air_length = asin(A_air_length);



3476    if ((rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain <= 0.0) || (rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain !=



3477         rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain_prev)) {



3478      rtDW->L1_xtrack_i = 0.0;



3479      rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain_prev = rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain;



3480    } else {



3481      if (fabs(A_air_length) < 0.087266462599716474) {



3482        rtDW->L1_xtrack_i += A_air_length * rtDW->L1_xtrack_i_gain * rtDW->dt;



3483        AB_length = rtDW->L1_xtrack_i;



3484        if (rtDW->L1_xtrack_i < -0.1) {



3485          rtDW->L1_xtrack_i = -0.1;



3486        }



3487



3488        if (AB_length > 0.1) {



3489          rtDW->L1_xtrack_i = 0.1;



3490        }



3491      }



3492    }



3493



3494    A_air_length += rtDW->L1_xtrack_i;



3495    A_air_length = wrap_PI(rt_atan2d_snf(rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * AB_0 -



3496      rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * AB[0], rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * AB[0] +



3497      rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] * AB_0) + A_air_length);



3498    break;



3499  }



3500



3501  A_air_length = prevent_indecision(A_air_length, &target_bearing_cd, rtDW);



3502  rtDW->last_Nu = A_air_length;



3503  target_bearing_cd = A_air_length;



3504  if (A_air_length < -1.5708) {



3505    A_air_length = -1.5708;



3506  }



3507



3508  if (target_bearing_cd > 1.5708) {



3509    A_air_length = 1.5708;



3510  }



3511



3512  rtDW->latAccDem = 4.0 * rtDW->L1_damping * rtDW->L1_damping * groundSpeed *



3513    groundSpeed / L1_dist * sin(A_air_length);



3514}

3516/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



3517static void update_loiter(const real_T b_center_WP[2], real_T b_radius, real_T



3518  b_loiter_direction, DW *rtDW)



3519{



3520  real_T omega;



3521  real_T A_air[2];



3522  real_T sanitized_bank_limit;



3523  real_T lateral_accel_sea_level;



3524  real_T eas2tas_sq;



3525  real_T amt;



3526  real_T target_bearing_cd;



3527  real_T tmp;



3528  omega = fabs(b_radius);



3529  sanitized_bank_limit = rtDW->loiter_bank_limit;



3530  if (rtDW->loiter_bank_limit < 0.0) {



3531    sanitized_bank_limit = 0.0;



3532  }



3533



3534  if (rtDW->loiter_bank_limit > 89.0) {



3535    sanitized_bank_limit = 89.0;



3536  }



3537



3538  lateral_accel_sea_level = tan(sanitized_bank_limit / 180.0 *



3539    3.1415926535897931) * rtDW->GRAVITY_MSS;



3540  eas2tas_sq = rtDW->EAS2TAS * rtDW->EAS2TAS;



3541  if ((sanitized_bank_limit == 0.0) || (rtDW->EAS_dem == 0.0) ||



3542      (lateral_accel_sea_level == 0.0)) {



3543    b_radius = omega * eas2tas_sq;



3544  } else {



3545    sanitized_bank_limit = rtDW->EAS_dem * rtDW->EAS_dem /



3546      lateral_accel_sea_level;



3547    if (sanitized_bank_limit > omega) {



3548      b_radius = omega * eas2tas_sq;



3549    } else {



3550      b_radius = fmax(sanitized_bank_limit * eas2tas_sq, omega);



3551    }



3552  }



3553



3554  omega = 6.2832 / rtDW->L1_period;



3555  eas2tas_sq = norm(rtDW->groundspeed_vector);



3556  sanitized_bank_limit = fmax(eas2tas_sq, 1.0);



3557  target_bearing_cd = get_bearing_to(b_center_WP, rtDW->current_loc, rtDW);



3558  lateral_accel_sea_level = cos(b_center_WP[0] * 1.0E-7 / rtDW->HD);



3559  if (lateral_accel_sea_level < 0.01) {



3560    lateral_accel_sea_level = 0.01;



3561  }



3562



3563  A_air[0] = (rtDW->current_loc[0] - b_center_WP[0]) *



3564    rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR;



3565  A_air[1] = (rtDW->current_loc[1] - b_center_WP[1]) *



3566    rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR * lateral_accel_sea_level;



3567  lateral_accel_sea_level = norm(A_air);



3568  if (lateral_accel_sea_level > 0.1) {



3569    A_air[0] /= lateral_accel_sea_level;



3570    A_air[1] /= lateral_accel_sea_level;



3571  } else if (eas2tas_sq < 0.1) {



3572    A_air[0] = cos(rtDW->yaw);



3573    A_air[1] = sin(rtDW->yaw);



3574  } else {



3575    A_air[0] = rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] / eas2tas_sq;



3576    A_air[1] = rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] / eas2tas_sq;



3577  }



3578



3579  eas2tas_sq = A_air[0] * rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] - A_air[1] *



3580    rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0];



3581  tmp = rtDW->groundspeed_vector[0] * A_air[0] + rtDW->groundspeed_vector[1] *



3582    A_air[1];



3583  target_bearing_cd = prevent_indecision(rt_atan2d_snf(eas2tas_sq, -tmp),



3584    &target_bearing_cd, rtDW);



3585  rtDW->last_Nu = target_bearing_cd;



3586  amt = target_bearing_cd;



3587  if (target_bearing_cd < -1.5707963267948966) {



3588    target_bearing_cd = -1.5707963267948966;



3589  }



3590



3591  if (amt > 1.5707963267948966) {



3592    target_bearing_cd = 1.5707963267948966;



3593  }



3594



3595  sanitized_bank_limit = 4.0 * rtDW->L1_damping * rtDW->L1_damping *



3596    sanitized_bank_limit * sanitized_bank_limit / (0.3183099 * rtDW->L1_damping *



3597    rtDW->L1_period * sanitized_bank_limit) * sin(target_bearing_cd);



3598  lateral_accel_sea_level -= b_radius;



3599  omega = 2.0 * rtDW->L1_damping * omega * tmp + omega * omega *



3600    lateral_accel_sea_level;



3601  eas2tas_sq *= b_loiter_direction;



3602  if ((-tmp < 0.0) && (eas2tas_sq < 0.0)) {



3603    omega = fmax(omega, 0.0);



3604  }



3605



3606  omega = (eas2tas_sq * eas2tas_sq / fmax(0.5 * b_radius, b_radius +



3607            lateral_accel_sea_level) + omega) * b_loiter_direction;



3608  if ((lateral_accel_sea_level > 0.0) && (b_loiter_direction *



3609       sanitized_bank_limit < b_loiter_direction * omega)) {



3610    rtDW->latAccDem = sanitized_bank_limit;



3611  } else {



3612    rtDW->latAccDem = omega;



3613  }



3614}

3811/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



3812static void copter_run(DW *rtDW)



3813{



3814  real_T temp_yaw_rate;



3815  real_T b_pitch;



3816  real_T output;



3817  if (fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[0]) > 0.0) {



3818    temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



3819  } else if (fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[1]) > 0.0) {



3820    temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



3821  } else if (fabs(rtDW->target_yaw_rate) > 0.0) {



3822    temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



3823  } else {



3824    temp_yaw_rate = get_weathervane_yaw_rate_cds(rtDW);



3825  }



3826



3827  b_pitch = rtDW->pitch_target / 100.0;



3828  if (b_pitch > rtDW->vel_forward_min_pitch) {



3829    rtDW->vel_forward_last_pct = 0.0;



3830    rtDW->tail_tilt = 0.0;



3831  } else {



3832    b_pitch -= rtDW->vel_forward_min_pitch;



3833    b_pitch = b_pitch / 25.0 * rtDW->vel_forward_gain;



3834    output = b_pitch;



3835    if (b_pitch < -1.0) {



3836      output = -1.0;



3837    }



3838



3839    if (b_pitch > 0.0) {



3840      output = 0.0;



3841    }



3842



3843    rtDW->vel_forward_last_pct = 0.98 * rtDW->vel_forward_last_pct + 0.02 *



3844      output;



3845    rtDW->tail_tilt = rtDW->vel_forward_last_pct *



3846      rtDW->vel_forward_tail_tilt_max;



3847  }



3848



3849  update_vel_controller_xy(rtDW);



3850  update_z_controller(rtDW);



3851  input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target,



3852    rtDW->target_yaw_rate + temp_yaw_rate, rtDW);



3853  rate_controller_run(rtDW);



3854  if (rtDW->aspeed > rtDW->aspeed_cp) {



3855    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_target;



3856    rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_target;



3857    stabilize(rtDW);



3858    rtDW->k_aileron *= rtDW->p_plane_cp;



3859    rtDW->k_elevator *= rtDW->p_plane_cp;



3860    rtDW->k_rudder *= rtDW->p_plane_cp;



3861  } else {



3862    rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



3863    rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



3864    rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



3865  }



3866



3867  AP_MotorsMulticopter_output(rtDW);



3868}

3884/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



3885static void set_alt_target_from_climb_rat_a(real_T alt_cm, real_T

3892  accel_z_cms = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z;



3893  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] < rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN) &&



3894      (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN != 0.0)) {



3895    accel_z_cms = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z * rtDW->POSCONTROL_OVERSPEED_GAIN_Z *



3896      rtDW->vel_desired[2] / rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN;



3897  }



3898



3899  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] > rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP) &&



3900      (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP != 0.0)) {



3901    accel_z_cms = accel_z_cms * rtDW->POSCONTROL_OVERSPEED_GAIN_Z *



3902      rtDW->vel_desired[2] / rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP;



3903  }



3904



3905  alt_change = accel_z_cms;



3906  if (accel_z_cms < 0.0) {



3907    accel_z_cms = 0.0;



3908  }



3909



3910  if (alt_change > 750.0) {



3911    accel_z_cms = 750.0;



3912  }



3913



3914  jerk_z = accel_z_cms * rtDW->POSCONTROL_JERK_RATIO;



3915  alt_change = (alt_cm - rtDW->pos_target[2]) * 6.0;



3916  if (alt_change < 0.0) {



3917    climb_rate_cms_temp = -1.0;



3918  } else if (alt_change > 0.0) {



3919    climb_rate_cms_temp = 1.0;



3920  } else if (alt_change == 0.0) {



3921    climb_rate_cms_temp = 0.0;



3922  } else {



3923    climb_rate_cms_temp = (rtNaN);



3924  }



3925



3926  b_climb_rate_cms *= climb_rate_cms_temp;



3927  rtDW->accel_last_z_cms += jerk_z * b_dt;



3928  rtDW->accel_last_z_cms = fmin(fmin(accel_z_cms, sqrt(fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[2]



3929    - b_climb_rate_cms) * 2.0 * jerk_z)), rtDW->accel_last_z_cms);



3930  jerk_z = rtDW->accel_last_z_cms * b_dt;



3931  accel_z_cms = rtDW->vel_desired[2] - jerk_z;



3932  jerk_z += rtDW->vel_desired[2];



3933  climb_rate_cms_temp = b_climb_rate_cms;



3934  if (b_climb_rate_cms < accel_z_cms) {



3935    climb_rate_cms_temp = accel_z_cms;



3936  }



3937



3938  if (b_climb_rate_cms > jerk_z) {



3939    climb_rate_cms_temp = jerk_z;



3940  }



3941



3942  accel_z_cms = fabs(climb_rate_cms_temp);



3943  rtDW->vel_desired[2] = alt_change;



3944  if (alt_change < -accel_z_cms) {



3945    rtDW->vel_desired[2] = -accel_z_cms;



3946  }



3947



3948  if (alt_change > accel_z_cms) {



3949    rtDW->vel_desired[2] = accel_z_cms;



3950  }



3951



3952  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] < 0.0) && ((!(rtDW->throttle_lower != 0.0)) ||



3953       (force_descend != 0.0))) {



3954    rtDW->pos_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2] * b_dt;



3955  } else {



3956    if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] > 0.0) && ((!(rtDW->throttle_upper != 0.0)) &&



3957         (!(rtDW->limit_pos_up != 0.0)))) {



3958      rtDW->pos_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2] * b_dt;



3959    }



3960  }



3961}

3963/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



3964static void plane_run_4a1(DW *rtDW)



3965{



3966  real_T commanded_pitch;



3967  update_50hz(rtDW);



3968  update_pitch_throttle(rtDW->hgt_dem_cm, rtDW->EAS_dem_cm,



3969                        rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor, rtDW);



3970  commanded_pitch = rtDW->pitch_dem * rtDW->HD * 100.0;



3971  rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = commanded_pitch;



3972  if (commanded_pitch < rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd) {



3973    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd;



3974  }



3975



3976  if (commanded_pitch > rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd) {



3977    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd;



3978  }



3979



3980  calc_nav_roll(rtDW);



3981  rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



3982  stabilize(rtDW);



3983  output_to_motors_plane_4a1(rtDW);



3984}

3993    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd;



3994  }



3995



3996  if (commanded_pitch > rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd) {



3997    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd;



3998  }



3999}

4001/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



4002static void get_distance_NE(const real_T loc2[2], const real_T b_loc[2], real_T



4003  distance_NE[2], DW *rtDW)



4004{



4005  real_T x;



4006  x = cos(b_loc[0] * 1.0E-7 / rtDW->HD);

4009  }

4012  distance_NE[1] = (loc2[1] - b_loc[1]) * rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR * x;



4013}

4331        AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



4332      } else {



4333        if (rtDW->pitch_target > 0.0) {



4334          rtDW->pitch_target = 0.0;



4335        }



4336



4337        update_z_controller(rtDW);



4338        input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target +



4339          rtDW->p_tilt_pitch_target * -3000.0, rtDW->target_yaw_rate, rtDW);



4340        rate_controller_run(rtDW);



4341        rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_inint;



4342        rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



4343        rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



4344        rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



4345        AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



4346      }



4347    }



4348    break;



4349



4350   case Fix2Rotor_Mode:



4351    if (rtDW->PathMode_g != Fix2Rotor_Mode) {



4352      rtDW->PathMode_g = Fix2Rotor_Mode;



4353      rtDW->uavMode_j = 0.0;



4354      rtDW->pos_target[2] = rtDW->curr_alt;



4355      rtDW->vel_desired[2] = 0.0;



4356      from_rotation_matrix(rtDW->rot_body_to_ned, rtDW->attitude_target_quat);



4357      rtDW->target_yaw_rate = 0.0;



4358      rtDW->tail_tilt = rtDW->tail_tilt_p2c;



4359      rtDW->roll_target = 0.0;



4360      rtDW->pitch_target = rtDW->pitch_target_p2c;



4361      rtDW->k_throttle = 0.0;



4362      rtDW->throttle_filter = 0.0;



4363    }



4364



4365    update_z_controller(rtDW);



4366    input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target,



4367      rtDW->target_yaw_rate, rtDW);



4368    rate_controller_run(rtDW);



4369    if (rtDW->aspeed > rtDW->aspeed_c2p) {



4370      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_target;



4371      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_target;



4372      stabilize(rtDW);



4373      rtDW->k_aileron *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



4374      rtDW->k_elevator *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



4375      rtDW->k_rudder *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



4376      TAS_dem = rtDW->yaw_in;



4377      if (rtDW->yaw_in < -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



4378        rtDW->yaw_in = -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



4379      }



4380



4381      if (TAS_dem > rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



4382        rtDW->yaw_in = rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



4383      }



4384



4385      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_inint;



4386      AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



4387    } else {



4388      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_inint;



4389      rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



4390      rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



4391      rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



4392      AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



4393    }



4394    break;



4395



4396   case PathFollowMode:



4397    if (rtDW->PathMode_g != PathFollowMode) {



4398      rtDW->PathMode_g = PathFollowMode;



4399      rtDW->uavMode_j = 1.0;



4400      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



4401      rtDW->center_WP[0] = rtDW->current_loc[0];



4402      rtDW->center_WP[1] = rtDW->current_loc[1];



4403    }



4404



4405    TAS_dem = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd - rtDW->hgt_dem_cm;



4406    if (TAS_dem > 8.0) {



4407      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



4408      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



4409    } else if (TAS_dem < -8.0) {



4410      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = -rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



4411      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



4412    } else {



4413      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = 0.0;



4414      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd;



4415    }



4416



4417    tmp = (int32_T)rtDW->WP_i_a - 1;



4418    prev_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[tmp];



4419    prev_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[tmp];



4420    tmp = (int32_T)(rtDW->WP_i_a + 1.0) - 1;



4421    next_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[tmp];



4422    next_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[tmp];



4423    get_distance_NE(next_WP, rtDW->current_loc, AB, rtDW);



4424    if (norm(AB) < rtDW->L1_radius) {



4425      if (rtDW->loc.num[(int32_T)(rtDW->WP_i_a + 2.0) - 1] != 99.0) {



4426        rtDW->WP_i_a++;



4427      } else {



4428        rtDW->WP_i_a = 2.0;



4429      }



4430    }



4431



4432    update_waypoint(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW->dist_min, rtDW);



4433    plane_run_4a1(rtDW);



4434    break;



4435



4436   case GoHomeMode:



4437    if (rtDW->PathMode_g != GoHomeMode) {



4438      rtDW->PathMode_g = GoHomeMode;



4439      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



4440      rtDW->center_WP[0] = rtDW->current_loc[0];



4441      rtDW->center_WP[1] = rtDW->current_loc[1];



4442    }



4443



4444    TAS_dem = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd - rtDW->hgt_dem_cm;



4445    if (TAS_dem > 8.0) {



4446      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



4447      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



4448    } else if (TAS_dem < -8.0) {



4449      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = -rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



4450      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



4451    } else {



4452      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = 0.0;



4453      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd;



4454    }



4455



4456    tmp = (int32_T)rtDW->WP_i_a - 1;



4457    prev_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[tmp];



4458    prev_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[tmp];



4459    next_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[0];



4460    next_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[0];



4461    update_waypoint(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW->dist_min, rtDW);



4462    plane_run_4a1(rtDW);



4463    break;



4464



4465   default:



4466    copter_run(rtDW);



4467    break;



4468  }



4469}

4471/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



4472static void copter_run_4a1(DW *rtDW)



4473{



4474  real_T temp_yaw_rate;



4475  real_T b_pitch;



4476  real_T fwd_vel_error;



4477  if (fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[0]) > 0.0) {



4478    temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



4479  } else if (fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[1]) > 0.0) {



4480    temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



4481  } else if (fabs(rtDW->target_yaw_rate) > 0.0) {



4482    temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



4483  } else {



4484    temp_yaw_rate = get_weathervane_yaw_rate_cds(rtDW);



4485  }



4486



4487  b_pitch = rtDW->pitch_target / 100.0;



4488  fwd_vel_error = -(b_pitch - rtDW->vel_forward_min_pitch) / 15.0 * 0.3 * 0.5;



4489  if (b_pitch > 0.0) {



4490    fwd_vel_error = 0.0;



4491    rtDW->vel_forward_integrator *= 0.95;



4492  }



4493



4494  rtDW->vel_forward_integrator += fwd_vel_error * rtDW->dt *



4495    rtDW->vel_forward_gain;



4496  b_pitch = rtDW->vel_forward_integrator;



4497  if (rtDW->vel_forward_integrator < 0.0) {



4498    rtDW->vel_forward_integrator = 0.0;



4499  }



4500



4501  if (b_pitch > 0.4) {



4502    rtDW->vel_forward_integrator = 0.4;



4503  }



4504



4505  update_vel_controller_xy(rtDW);



4506  update_z_controller(rtDW);



4507  input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target,



4508    rtDW->target_yaw_rate + temp_yaw_rate, rtDW);



4509  rate_controller_run(rtDW);



4510  rtDW->tail_tilt = 0.0;



4511  rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->vel_forward_integrator;



4512  if (rtDW->aspeed > rtDW->aspeed_cp) {



4513    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_target;



4514    rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_target;



4515    stabilize(rtDW);



4516    rtDW->k_aileron *= rtDW->p_plane_cp;



4517    rtDW->k_elevator *= rtDW->p_plane_cp;



4518    rtDW->k_rudder *= rtDW->p_plane_cp;



4519  } else {



4520    rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



4521    rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



4522    rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



4523  }



4524



4525  AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



4526}

4528/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



4529static void set_alt_target_from_climb_rat_m(real_T b_climb_rate_cms, real_T b_dt,



4530  real_T force_descend, real_T sign_in, DW *rtDW)



4531{



4532  real_T accel_z_cms;



4533  real_T jerk_z;



4534  real_T sign_in_0;



4535  accel_z_cms = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z;



4536  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] < rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN) &&



4537      (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN != 0.0)) {



4538    accel_z_cms = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACCEL_Z * rtDW->POSCONTROL_OVERSPEED_GAIN_Z *



4539      rtDW->vel_desired[2] / rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_DOWN;



4540  }



4541



4542  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] > rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP) &&



4543      (rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP != 0.0)) {



4544    accel_z_cms = accel_z_cms * rtDW->POSCONTROL_OVERSPEED_GAIN_Z *



4545      rtDW->vel_desired[2] / rtDW->POSCONTROL_SPEED_UP;



4546  }



4547



4548  jerk_z = accel_z_cms;



4549  if (accel_z_cms < 0.0) {



4550    accel_z_cms = 0.0;



4551  }



4552



4553  if (jerk_z > 750.0) {



4554    accel_z_cms = 750.0;



4555  }



4556



4557  jerk_z = accel_z_cms * rtDW->POSCONTROL_JERK_RATIO;



4558  if (sign_in < 0.0) {



4559    sign_in_0 = -1.0;



4560  } else if (sign_in > 0.0) {



4561    sign_in_0 = 1.0;



4562  } else if (sign_in == 0.0) {



4563    sign_in_0 = 0.0;



4564  } else {



4565    sign_in_0 = (rtNaN);



4566  }



4567



4568  b_climb_rate_cms *= sign_in_0;



4569  rtDW->accel_last_z_cms += jerk_z * b_dt;



4570  rtDW->accel_last_z_cms = fmin(fmin(accel_z_cms, sqrt(fabs(rtDW->vel_desired[2]



4571    - b_climb_rate_cms) * 2.0 * jerk_z)), rtDW->accel_last_z_cms);



4572  jerk_z = rtDW->accel_last_z_cms * b_dt;



4573  accel_z_cms = rtDW->vel_desired[2] - jerk_z;



4574  jerk_z += rtDW->vel_desired[2];



4575  rtDW->vel_desired[2] = b_climb_rate_cms;



4576  if (b_climb_rate_cms < accel_z_cms) {



4577    rtDW->vel_desired[2] = accel_z_cms;



4578  }



4579



4580  if (b_climb_rate_cms > jerk_z) {



4581    rtDW->vel_desired[2] = jerk_z;



4582  }



4583



4584  if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] < 0.0) && ((!(rtDW->throttle_lower != 0.0)) ||



4585       (force_descend != 0.0))) {



4586    rtDW->pos_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2] * b_dt;



4587  } else {



4588    if ((rtDW->vel_desired[2] > 0.0) && ((!(rtDW->throttle_upper != 0.0)) &&



4589         (!(rtDW->limit_pos_up != 0.0)))) {



4590      rtDW->pos_target[2] += rtDW->vel_desired[2] * b_dt;



4591    }



4592  }



4593}

5213    }



5214



5215    if (-rtDW->tail_tilt > b_high) {



5216      throttle_in_error = b_high;



5217    }

5219    rtDW->tail_tilt += throttle_in_error;



5220    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_target;



5221    rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_target;



5222    stabilize(rtDW);



5223    rtDW->k_aileron *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



5224    rtDW->k_elevator *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



5225    rtDW->k_rudder *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;

5227    if (rtDW->yaw_in < -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



5228      rtDW->yaw_in = -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



5229    }

5231    if (pitch_target_temp > rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



5232      rtDW->yaw_in = rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



5233    }

5236    AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



5237    break;

5239   case VerticalMove:

5272      update_loiter(rtDW->center_WP, rtDW->radius, rtDW->loiter_direction, rtDW);



5273      plane_run_4a1(rtDW);



5274      break;



5275



5276     case 0:



5277      rtDW->pos_target[0] = 0.0;



5278      rtDW->loc_origin[0] = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.turnCenterLL[0];



5279      rtDW->pos_target[1] = 0.0;



5280      rtDW->loc_origin[1] = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.turnCenterLL[1];



5281      get_vector_xy_from_origin_NE(rtDW->current_loc, rtDW->loc_origin, a, rtDW);



5282      rtDW->curr_pos[0] = a[0] * 100.0;



5283      rtDW->curr_pos[1] = a[1] * 100.0;



5284      if (rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd - rtDW->pos_target[2] > 8.0) {



5285        rtDW->climb_rate_cms = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



5286        set_alt_target_from_climb_rate_(rtDW->climb_rate_cms, rtDW->dt, 0.0,



5287          rtDW);

5289        rtDW->climb_rate_cms = -rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;

5291          rtDW);

5638/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



5639static void setup_motors(DW *rtDW)



5640{



5641  rtDW->roll_factor[0] = -0.70710678118654746;



5642  rtDW->pitch_factor[0] = 0.70710678118654757;



5643  rtDW->yaw_factor[0] = rtDW->AP_MOTORS_MATRIX_YAW_FACTOR_CW;



5644  rtDW->roll_factor[1] = 0.70710678118654757;



5645  rtDW->pitch_factor[1] = -0.70710678118654746;



5646  rtDW->yaw_factor[1] = rtDW->AP_MOTORS_MATRIX_YAW_FACTOR_CW * 2.5599;



5647  rtDW->roll_factor[2] = 0.70710678118654757;



5648  rtDW->pitch_factor[2] = 0.70710678118654757;



5649  rtDW->yaw_factor[2] = rtDW->AP_MOTORS_MATRIX_YAW_FACTOR_CCW;



5650  rtDW->roll_factor[3] = -0.70710678118654768;



5651  rtDW->pitch_factor[3] = -0.70710678118654746;



5652  rtDW->yaw_factor[3] = rtDW->AP_MOTORS_MATRIX_YAW_FACTOR_CCW * 2.5599;



5653  rtDW->pitch_factor[3] *= rtDW->Kx + 1.0;



5654  rtDW->pitch_factor[0] *= 1.0 - rtDW->Kx;



5655  rtDW->pitch_factor[1] *= rtDW->Kx + 1.0;



5656  rtDW->pitch_factor[2] *= 1.0 - rtDW->Kx;



5657}
