5659/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



5660static void output_to_motors_plane(DW *rtDW)



5661{



5662  real_T thrust_dt;



5663  real_T pwm_out_temp;



5664  real_T low;



5665  real_T thrust_dt_tmp;



5666  rtDW->tail_tilt = -9556.0;



5667  thrust_dt_tmp = rtDW->pwm_max - rtDW->pwm_min;



5668  thrust_dt = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->dt / rtDW->thrust_slew_time;



5669  thrust_dt_tmp = thrust_dt_tmp * rtDW->k_throttle + rtDW->pwm_min;



5670  low = rtDW->pwm_out[1] - thrust_dt;



5671  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[1] + thrust_dt;



5672  rtDW->pwm_out[1] = thrust_dt_tmp;



5673  if (thrust_dt_tmp < low) {



5674    rtDW->pwm_out[1] = low;



5675  }



5676



5677  if (thrust_dt_tmp > pwm_out_temp) {



5678    rtDW->pwm_out[1] = pwm_out_temp;



5679  }



5680



5681  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[1];



5682  if (rtDW->pwm_out[1] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



5683    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



5684  }



5685



5686  if (rtDW->pwm_out[1] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



5687    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



5688  }



5689



5690  rtDW->pwm_out[1] = pwm_out_temp;



5691  low = rtDW->pwm_out[3] - thrust_dt;



5692  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[3] + thrust_dt;



5693  rtDW->pwm_out[3] = thrust_dt_tmp;



5694  if (thrust_dt_tmp < low) {



5695    rtDW->pwm_out[3] = low;



5696  }



5697



5698  if (thrust_dt_tmp > pwm_out_temp) {



5699    rtDW->pwm_out[3] = pwm_out_temp;



5700  }



5701



5702  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[3];



5703  if (rtDW->pwm_out[3] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



5704    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



5705  }



5706



5707  if (rtDW->pwm_out[3] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



5708    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



5709  }



5710



5711  rtDW->pwm_out[3] = pwm_out_temp;



5712  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[0] - thrust_dt;



5713  low = rtDW->pwm_out[0] + thrust_dt;



5714  rtDW->pwm_out[0] = rtDW->pwm_min;



5715  if (rtDW->pwm_min < pwm_out_temp) {



5716    rtDW->pwm_out[0] = pwm_out_temp;



5717  }



5718



5719  if (rtDW->pwm_min > low) {



5720    rtDW->pwm_out[0] = low;



5721  }



5722



5723  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[0];



5724  if (rtDW->pwm_out[0] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



5725    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



5726  }



5727



5728  if (rtDW->pwm_out[0] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



5729    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



5730  }



5731



5732  rtDW->pwm_out[0] = pwm_out_temp;



5733  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[2] - thrust_dt;



5734  low = rtDW->pwm_out[2] + thrust_dt;



5735  rtDW->pwm_out[2] = rtDW->pwm_min;



5736  if (rtDW->pwm_min < pwm_out_temp) {



5737    rtDW->pwm_out[2] = pwm_out_temp;



5738  }



5739



5740  if (rtDW->pwm_min > low) {



5741    rtDW->pwm_out[2] = low;



5742  }



5743



5744  pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_out[2];



5745  if (rtDW->pwm_out[2] < rtDW->pwm_min) {



5746    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_min;



5747  }



5748



5749  if (rtDW->pwm_out[2] > rtDW->pwm_max) {



5750    pwm_out_temp = rtDW->pwm_max;



5751  }



5752



5753  rtDW->pwm_out[2] = pwm_out_temp;



5754}

5756/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



5757static void plane_run(DW *rtDW)



5758{



5759  real_T commanded_pitch;



5760  update_50hz(rtDW);



5761  update_pitch_throttle(rtDW->hgt_dem_cm, rtDW->EAS_dem_cm,



5762                        rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor, rtDW);



5763  commanded_pitch = rtDW->pitch_dem * rtDW->HD * 100.0;



5764  rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = commanded_pitch;



5765  if (commanded_pitch < rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd) {



5766    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd;



5767  }



5768



5769  if (commanded_pitch > rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd) {



5770    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd;



5771  }



5772



5773  calc_nav_roll(rtDW);



5774  rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



5775  stabilize(rtDW);



5776  output_to_motors_plane(rtDW);



5777}

6127      input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target +



6128        rtDW->p_tilt_pitch_target * tail_error, rtDW->target_yaw_rate, rtDW);



6129      rate_controller_run(rtDW);



6130      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_inint;



6131      rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



6132      rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



6133      rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



6134      AP_MotorsMulticopter_output(rtDW);



6135    }



6136    break;



6137



6138   case Fix2Rotor_Mode:



6139    if (rtDW->PathMode != Fix2Rotor_Mode) {



6140      rtDW->PathMode = Fix2Rotor_Mode;



6141      rtDW->uavMode = 0.0;



6142      rtDW->pos_target[2] = rtDW->curr_alt;



6143      rtDW->vel_desired[2] = 0.0;



6144      from_rotation_matrix(rtDW->rot_body_to_ned, rtDW->attitude_target_quat);



6145      rtDW->target_yaw_rate = 0.0;



6146      rtDW->tail_tilt = rtDW->tail_tilt_p2c;



6147      rtDW->roll_target = 0.0;



6148      rtDW->pitch_target = 0.0;



6149    }



6150



6151    update_z_controller(rtDW);



6152    tail_error = rtDW->tail_tilt;



6153    if (rtDW->tail_tilt < -3000.0) {



6154      tail_error = -3000.0;



6155    }



6156



6157    if (rtDW->tail_tilt > 700.0) {



6158      tail_error = 700.0;



6159    }



6160



6161    input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target +



6162      rtDW->p_tilt_pitch_target * tail_error, rtDW->target_yaw_rate, rtDW);



6163    rate_controller_run(rtDW);



6164    if (fabs(-rtDW->tail_tilt) > 100.0) {



6165      rtDW->throttle_filter = 0.0;



6166      rtDW->throttle_in = 0.0;



6167    }



6168



6169    amt = -rtDW->tail_tilt_rate * rtDW->dt;



6170    low = rtDW->tail_tilt_rate * rtDW->dt;



6171    tail_error = -rtDW->tail_tilt;



6172    if (-rtDW->tail_tilt < amt) {



6173      tail_error = amt;



6174    }



6175



6176    if (-rtDW->tail_tilt > low) {



6177      tail_error = low;



6178    }



6179



6180    rtDW->tail_tilt += tail_error;



6181    if (rtDW->aspeed > rtDW->aspeed_c2p) {



6182      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_target;



6183      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_target;



6184      stabilize(rtDW);



6185      rtDW->k_aileron *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



6186      rtDW->k_elevator *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



6187      rtDW->k_rudder *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



6188      tail_error = rtDW->yaw_in;



6189      if (rtDW->yaw_in < -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



6190        rtDW->yaw_in = -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



6191      }



6192



6193      if (tail_error > rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



6194        rtDW->yaw_in = rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



6195      }



6196



6197      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_c2p;



6198      AP_MotorsMulticopter_output(rtDW);



6199    } else {



6200      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_inint;



6201      rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



6202      rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



6203      rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



6204      AP_MotorsMulticopter_output(rtDW);



6205    }



6206    break;



6207



6208   case PathFollowMode:



6209    if (rtDW->PathMode != PathFollowMode) {



6210      rtDW->PathMode = PathFollowMode;



6211      rtDW->uavMode = 1.0;



6212      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



6213      rtDW->center_WP[0] = rtDW->current_loc[0];



6214      rtDW->center_WP[1] = rtDW->current_loc[1];



6215    }



6216



6217    tail_error = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd - rtDW->hgt_dem_cm;



6218    if (tail_error > 8.0) {



6219      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



6220      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



6221    } else if (tail_error < -8.0) {



6222      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = -rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



6223      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



6224    } else {



6225      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = 0.0;



6226      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd;



6227    }



6228



6229    tmp = (int32_T)rtDW->WP_i_o - 1;



6230    prev_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[tmp];



6231    prev_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[tmp];



6232    tmp = (int32_T)(rtDW->WP_i_o + 1.0) - 1;



6233    next_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[tmp];



6234    next_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[tmp];



6235    get_distance_NE(next_WP, rtDW->current_loc, AB, rtDW);



6236    if (norm(AB) < rtDW->L1_radius) {



6237      if (rtDW->loc.num[(int32_T)(rtDW->WP_i_o + 2.0) - 1] != 99.0) {



6238        rtDW->WP_i_o++;



6239      } else {



6240        rtDW->WP_i_o = 2.0;



6241      }



6242    }



6243



6244    update_waypoint(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW->dist_min, rtDW);



6245    plane_run(rtDW);



6246    break;



6247



6248   case GoHomeMode:



6249    if (rtDW->PathMode != GoHomeMode) {



6250      rtDW->PathMode = GoHomeMode;



6251      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



6252      rtDW->center_WP[0] = rtDW->current_loc[0];



6253      rtDW->center_WP[1] = rtDW->current_loc[1];



6254    }



6255



6256    tail_error = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd - rtDW->hgt_dem_cm;



6257    if (tail_error > 8.0) {



6258      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



6259      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



6260    } else if (tail_error < -8.0) {



6261      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = -rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.maxClimbSpeed;



6262      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



6263    } else {



6264      rtDW->climb_rate_cms = 0.0;



6265      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->PathModeOut_sl.heightCmd;



6266    }



6267



6268    tmp = (int32_T)rtDW->WP_i_o - 1;



6269    prev_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[tmp];



6270    prev_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[tmp];



6271    next_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[0];



6272    next_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[0];



6273    update_waypoint(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW->dist_min, rtDW);



6274    plane_run(rtDW);



6275    break;



6276



6277   default:



6278    copter_run(rtDW);



6279    break;



6280  }



6281}

6283/* Function for MATLAB Function: '<Root>/input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_euler_rate_yaw4' */



6284static void copter_run_posfree(DW *rtDW)



6285{



6286  update_z_controller(rtDW);



6287  rtDW->roll_target = 0.0;



6288  rtDW->pitch_target = 0.0;



6289  rtDW->target_yaw_rate = 0.0;



6290  input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target,



6291    rtDW->target_yaw_rate, rtDW);



6292  rate_controller_run(rtDW);



6293  rtDW->tail_tilt = 0.0;



6294  rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



6295  rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



6296  rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



6297  AP_MotorsMulticopter_output(rtDW);



6298}

7496      rtDW->roll_target_pilot / 10.0 * vel_desired_tmp;



7497    if (fabs(rtDW->pitch_target_pilot) > 0.0) {



7498      temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



7499    } else if (fabs(rtDW->roll_target_pilot) > 0.0) {



7500      temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



7501    } else if (fabs(rtDW->target_yaw_rate) > 0.0) {



7502      temp_yaw_rate = 0.0;



7503    } else {



7504      temp_yaw_rate = get_weathervane_yaw_rate_cds(rtDW);



7505    }



7506



7507    set_alt_target_from_climb_rate_(rtDW->climb_rate_cms, rtDW->dt, 0.0, rtDW);



7508    update_vel_controller_xy(rtDW);



7509    update_z_controller(rtDW);



7510    input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target,



7511      rtDW->target_yaw_rate + temp_yaw_rate, rtDW);



7512    rate_controller_run(rtDW);



7513    AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



7514    break;



7515



7516   case 4:



7517    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 4.0) {



7518      rtDW->mode_state_c = 4.0;



7519    }



7520



7521    calc_nav_roll(rtDW);



7522    rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



7523    stabilize(rtDW);



7524    output_to_motors_plane_4a1(rtDW);



7525    break;



7526



7527   case 5:



7528    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 5.0) {



7529      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->height * 100.0;



7530      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



7531      rtDW->mode_state_c = 5.0;



7532    } else {



7533      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



7534    }



7535



7536    update_50hz(rtDW);



7537    update_pitch_throttle(rtDW->hgt_dem_cm, rtDW->EAS_dem_cm,



7538                          rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor, rtDW);



7539    temp_yaw_rate = rtDW->pitch_dem * rtDW->HD * 100.0;



7540    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = temp_yaw_rate;



7541    if (temp_yaw_rate < rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd) {



7542      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd;



7543    }



7544



7545    if (temp_yaw_rate > rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd) {



7546      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd;



7547    }



7548



7549    calc_nav_roll(rtDW);



7550    rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



7551    stabilize(rtDW);



7552    output_to_motors_plane_4a1(rtDW);



7553    break;



7554



7555   case 6:



7556    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 6.0) {



7557      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->height * 100.0;



7558      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



7559      rtDW->mode_state_c = 6.0;



7560    } else {



7561      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



7562    }



7563



7564    prev_WP_tmp = (int32_T)rtDW->WP_i_h - 1;



7565    prev_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[prev_WP_tmp];



7566    prev_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[prev_WP_tmp];



7567    prev_WP_tmp = (int32_T)(rtDW->WP_i_h + 1.0) - 1;



7568    next_WP[0] = rtDW->loc.lat[prev_WP_tmp];



7569    next_WP[1] = rtDW->loc.lon[prev_WP_tmp];



7570    temp_yaw_rate = cos(rtDW->current_loc[0] * 1.0E-7 / rtDW->HD);



7571    if (temp_yaw_rate < 0.01) {



7572      temp_yaw_rate = 0.01;



7573    }



7574



7575    next_WP_0[0] = (rtDW->loc.lat[prev_WP_tmp] - rtDW->current_loc[0]) *



7576      rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR;



7577    next_WP_0[1] = (rtDW->loc.lon[prev_WP_tmp] - rtDW->current_loc[1]) *



7578      rtDW->LOCATION_SCALING_FACTOR * temp_yaw_rate;



7579    if (norm(next_WP_0) < rtDW->L1_radius) {



7580      if (rtDW->loc.num[(int32_T)(rtDW->WP_i_h + 2.0) - 1] != 99.0) {



7581        rtDW->WP_i_h++;



7582      } else {



7583        rtDW->WP_i_h = 2.0;



7584      }



7585    }



7586



7587    update_50hz(rtDW);



7588    update_pitch_throttle(rtDW->hgt_dem_cm, rtDW->EAS_dem_cm,



7589                          rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor, rtDW);



7590    update_waypoint(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW->dist_min, rtDW);



7591    temp_yaw_rate = rtDW->pitch_dem * rtDW->HD * 100.0;



7592    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = temp_yaw_rate;



7593    if (temp_yaw_rate < rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd) {



7594      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd;



7595    }



7596



7597    if (temp_yaw_rate > rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd) {



7598      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd;



7599    }



7600



7601    calc_nav_roll(rtDW);



7602    rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



7603    stabilize(rtDW);



7604    output_to_motors_plane_4a1(rtDW);



7605    break;



7606



7607   case 7:



7608    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 7.0) {



7609      rtDW->pos_target[2] = rtDW->curr_alt;



7610      rtDW->vel_desired[2] = 0.0;



7611      rtDW->mode_state_c = 7.0;



7612      rtDW->k_throttle = 0.0;



7613      from_rotation_matrix(rtDW->rot_body_to_ned, rtDW->attitude_target_quat);



7614    }



7615



7616    set_alt_target_from_climb_rate_(rtDW->climb_rate_cms, rtDW->dt, 0.0, rtDW);



7617    update_z_controller(rtDW);



7618    input_euler_angle_roll_pitch_eu(rtDW->roll_target, rtDW->pitch_target,



7619      rtDW->target_yaw_rate, rtDW);



7620    rate_controller_run(rtDW);



7621    if (rtDW->aspeed > rtDW->aspeed_c2p) {



7622      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_target;



7623      rtDW->nav_roll_cd = rtDW->roll_target;



7624      stabilize(rtDW);



7625      rtDW->k_aileron *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



7626      rtDW->k_elevator *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



7627      rtDW->k_rudder *= rtDW->p_plane_c2p;



7628      temp_yaw_rate = rtDW->yaw_in;



7629      if (rtDW->yaw_in < -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



7630        rtDW->yaw_in = -rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



7631      }



7632



7633      if (temp_yaw_rate > rtDW->yaw_max_c2p) {



7634        rtDW->yaw_in = rtDW->yaw_max_c2p;



7635      }



7636



7637      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_c2p;



7638    } else {



7639      rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ = rtDW->POSCONTROL_ACC_Z_FILT_HZ_inint;



7640      rtDW->k_aileron = 0.0;



7641      rtDW->k_elevator = 0.0;



7642      rtDW->k_rudder = 0.0;



7643    }



7644



7645    rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



7646    AP_MotorsMulticopter_output_4a1(rtDW);



7647    break;



7648



7649   case 8:



7650    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 8.0) {



7651      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm = rtDW->height * 100.0;



7652      rtDW->inint_hgt = 1.0;



7653      rtDW->center_WP[0] = rtDW->current_loc[0];



7654      rtDW->center_WP[1] = rtDW->current_loc[1];



7655      rtDW->mode_state_c = 8.0;



7656    } else {



7657      rtDW->hgt_dem_cm += rtDW->dt * rtDW->climb_rate_cms;



7658    }



7659



7660    update_50hz(rtDW);



7661    update_pitch_throttle(rtDW->hgt_dem_cm, rtDW->EAS_dem_cm,



7662                          rtDW->aerodynamic_load_factor, rtDW);



7663    update_loiter(rtDW->center_WP, rtDW->radius, rtDW->loiter_direction, rtDW);



7664    temp_yaw_rate = rtDW->pitch_dem * rtDW->HD * 100.0;



7665    rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = temp_yaw_rate;



7666    if (temp_yaw_rate < rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd) {



7667      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_min_cd;



7668    }



7669



7670    if (temp_yaw_rate > rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd) {



7671      rtDW->nav_pitch_cd = rtDW->pitch_limit_max_cd;



7672    }



7673



7674    calc_nav_roll(rtDW);



7675    rtDW->k_throttle = rtDW->throttle_dem;



7676    stabilize(rtDW);



7677    output_to_motors_plane_4a1(rtDW);



7678    break;



7679



7680   case 9:



7681    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 9.0) {



7682      rtDW->mode_state_c = 9.0;



7683    }



7684



7685    auto_mode_4a1(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW);



7686    break;



7687



7688   case 10:



7689    if (rtDW->mode_state_c != 10.0) {



7690      rtDW->mode_state_c = 10.0;



7691    }



7692



7693    auto_mode_sl_4a1(prev_WP, next_WP, rtDW);



7694    break;



7695



7696   default:



7697    rtDW->mode_state_c = rtDW->mode;



7698    break;



7699  }



7700}
